Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中文字幕 - <font color=red>Zcc911@Douban</font>\NEnglish Subtitle - <font color="#ffff00">Aorion</font>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:01:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转载时请注明来源: <font color=red>Zcc911@Douban</font> & <font color="#ffff00">Aorion</font>\N耗神两天遍查资料+手打自译的双语字幕 请勿打击译者积极性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类经历了10万年\NIt took the earth's population a hundred thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才繁衍出10亿人口\Nto reach a billion people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在随后的100年 人口增长到20亿\NAnd then just, a hundred more to reach 2 billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再翻一番 只花了50年\NAnd only 50 years to double again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在70年代 人口增至40亿\Ndouble again to four billion in 1970.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 我们快要达到80亿了 80亿\NWe're nearly at 8 billion now. ... 8 billion now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正通过延长人均寿命的方式自我毁灭\NWe are destroying the very means by which life is extended.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一次全球性的瘟疫灾难都可以被归咎\NEvery single global ill that plagues the Earth can be traced back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被归咎于人口的过剩 人口过剩\Ntraced back to human overpopulation... human overpopulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们还不付诸行动\NWhat didn't we demand any action?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大量砍伐 倾倒垃圾 挥霍消费 肆意破坏\Nwe clear cut, we dump, we consume, we destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球上半数的动物物种业已消亡\NHalf the animal species on earth have vanished
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在过去40年里被灭绝 40年\Nvanished for the last 40 years... 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.38,0:01:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们仍在侵略自然环境\Nand still we keep attacking our own environment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非到大难临头 才得深刻教训 ... 留心关注\Nit doesn't take a catastrophe to learn our lesson... to get our attention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有痛苦方可改变行为\NNothing changes behaviour like pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,<font color=red>但丁密码 / 地狱 / 地狱解码 / Inferno</font>\N或许只有痛苦 才能拯救我们\NMaybe pain can save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个开关\NThere is a switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你打开\Nif you throw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球上半数人口会死亡\Nhalf the people on earth will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但反之 人类将在一百年内灭绝\NBut if you don't, the human race will be extinct in a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会怎么做\NWhat would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就像人体内的癌症\NMankind is the cancer in its own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有拯救芸芸众生的切肤博爱吗\NDo you love humanity enough to save it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防万一 他们捉住我\NIn case, they find me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你留下了一串指引\NI left you a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它是最艰险的征程\NThe hardest one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坎坷尽头 横亘炼狱\NInferno will be at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的应急计划\NYou are my contingency plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人类最后的希望\NYou are humanity's final hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请确保地狱的降临\NMake sure Inferno is unleashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 就寻见 (圣经 马太福音 第7章 第7节)\NSeek and find
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛罗伦萨巴迪亚教堂, 佛罗伦萨, 意大利\NBadia Fiorentina (Church), Florence, Italy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追了一路\NA long road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却跑来这里\Nbut here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相比美国人 我更棒些\NBetter me, than the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来你要向我坦白 它在哪里\NYou're going to want to tell me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 布沙尔先生\NYes, Mr. Bouchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我会的\NI know I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们\NTell them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是灾 地狱为解\N"Humanity is the disease, Inferno is the cure."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叛徒\NTraitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受难吧 罪人们 为汝之孽付出代价\NSuffer, you sinners. Pay for your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受难吧 罪人们 为汝之孽付出代价\NSuffer, you sinners. Pay for your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为汝之孽付出代价\NPay for your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受难吧 罪人们 为汝之孽付出代价\NSuffer, you sinners. Pay for your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢魂失魄\NRuin of souls...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 请稍等 - 怎么回事 ...\N- One moment, please - What is going ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 发生了什么 - 布鲁克斯医生\N- What is happening - Dr. Brooks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛弃所有的希望\NAbadon all hope
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有希望\NAll hope ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登先生 我是布鲁克斯医生\NMr. Langdon, I'm Dr. Brooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会做些检查 不必担心\NI'm going to do a few checks, nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们把它扔掉 好吗\NLet's get rid of this, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道今天是周几吗\NDo you know what day of the week it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周六\NSaturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天周一 6月28号\NIt's Monday, 28th of June.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周一 6月28号\NMonday, 28th of June.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道我们在哪儿吗\NDo you know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波士顿\NBoston.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻省总医院\NMassachusetts General (Hospital)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您最后能记起的事情是什么\NAnd what's the last thing you can remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 呃 我在校园里\NI uh... I was on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好模糊 我看不清楚\NEverything is blur. It's out of focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是遇到了什么意外\NWas I in some kind of an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会弄清楚的\NWe'll get to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有没有人需要帮忙通知的\NIs there someone we should call for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的妻子 家人\NYour Wife? Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 我没结婚\NNo. No. I'm not married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授 你的头部受创\NProfessor Langdon, you're suffering from a head trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您似乎有轻微的逆行性失忆\NYou appeared to have a mild retrograde amnesia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做了个CT扫瞄 没有发现颅内出血\NWe've done a CT scan, there's no evidence of intracranial bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都挺好 会恢复的\NWhich is very reassuring. Non-terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试着放松下来\NJust try to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神经系统方面 看样子没问题\NNeurologically, you seem to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的记忆会在随后几天恢复\NYour memory will return over the next several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们 ... 我们就安心静养吧\NSo we'll... we'll wait and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能麻烦你关下灯吗\NCould you turn off the lights please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是头部创伤严重 导致脑挫裂伤 那...\NIf the head trauma was bad enough to cause a cerebral contusion, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你 ... 麻烦你关下灯好吗\NCould you please ... Could you please turn off the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在 ... 佛罗伦萨 ... 来干什么\NWhat am I... doing... in Florence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个大教堂 是佛罗伦萨旧宫 对吗\NThat's a Duomo. That's the Palazzo Vecchio, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 ... 我怎么来这儿的\NHow... How did I get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3小时前 你头部带伤 跑来我们的急诊室\NYou came to our emergency room 3 hours ago with a head wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 ... 我是不是还有位女伴\NWas I... Was I with a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 一位出租车司机送您来的\NNo, a cab driver brought you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没拿钱包 没有手机 没带身份证\NNo wallet. No phone. No ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我名字\NHow do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱俩见过\NWe've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在伦敦帝国学院听过你的演讲 后面还聊了下\NI saw you lecture at the Church in Imperial College London, we spoke afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您待我很亲切\Nyou were very nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们见过\NWe've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 那样讲不大恰当\NSorry, that's not quite fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我9岁\NI was nine at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 9 9岁\NWait. Nine-nine years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时对拼图游戏很入迷\NI was crazy about puzzles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢您的书\NAnd I like your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许不是"失落的表意文字语言" 而是其他的\NMaybe not "Lost language of Ideograms", but the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全看了\NI read them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古怪的小年轻\NA weird kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如此\NI was actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚讲得很大声吗\NDid I say that out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\NYou did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉\NVery sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授 您的头疼症状一开始会比较强烈\NProfessor Langdon, your headaches are going to be intense initially.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也可能还会有恶心 糊涂 头昏等情况\NAnd you can also expect nausea, confusion and dizziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前台来的电话\NThat was the front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察来了 要见您\NThe police are here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 为什么\NMe, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在与他们交流之前 兰登教授 您应该了解一下您的真实情况\NBefore you talk to them, Professor Langdon, you should know the facts of your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您头部的创伤并非事故所致\NYour head wound was not caused by an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是枪击造成的\NIt was the result of a gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一枚子弹擦过您头骨顶端 您很可能还狠狠地摔了下来\NA bullet grazed the top of your skull and you most likely took a bad fall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是导致脑震荡的原因\Nwhich is what caused the concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果子弹再往里一英吋\NIf the bullet had been an inch to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就真的要命了\Nit could have killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快点儿\NCome on, Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 这边 快\NThis way. This way, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租车\NTaxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来\NGet in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 你们喝醉了吗\NWhat, are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加速 开快点\NStep on it. Floor it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 出了啥事 - 我不知道\N- What's going on? - I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会比较疼\NThis is gonna hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系\NIt's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特\NRobert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 就寻见\NSeek and find.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 就必寻见\N佛罗伦萨 意大利 凌晨 4:52\NSeek and find.\NFlorence, Italy 4:52 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿是我的住处\NThis is my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你仍在佛罗伦萨\NYou're still in Florence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要打电话叫警察\NI'm going to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会 那个女警刚刚才试着杀掉咱们\NWait. That policewoman just tried to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们打给美国领事馆 如果你没意见的话\NWe will call the U.S. Consulate instead if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先慢着 让我 ... 让我歇会\NJust... wait. Just give me... give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 整理下情况 - 为什么会有人射杀你\N- Get a hold on things - Why was someone shooting at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你进急诊室时\NAlso, when you came into ER,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在反覆喃喃些什么\Nyou were mumbling something over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱 ... 非常抱歉\NVery sorr... Very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉\NVery sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你当时为什么要讲这些吗\NDo you have any idea why you would be saying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不知道 - 为什么有人要射杀你\N- No. - Why was someone shooting at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以继续对我追问这些 女士\NYou can keep asking me these questions, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也不知道答案是什么\NBut I'm not going to know these answers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫西恩娜\NMy name is Sienna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚问了很多问题\NYou just asked a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我感觉我现在非常玻璃心\NYeah, I'm feeling a tad vulnerable right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在身旁待着一个正被追杀的人\NI'm with someone other people want to shoot at!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些问题很重要\NQuestions are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能记起来\NAnd I hope you recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以再要 ... 一杯\NCan I ask you for a... cup of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 棕色的 热的\NWhat? It's brown and it's... hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们早上喝来补充能量的 呃\NPeople drink it in the morning for energy. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶\NTea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶 不 另一种\NTea. No. The other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 咖啡 - 咖啡\N- Coffee. - Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能要一杯咖啡吗\NCould I have a cup of coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你整理得很好\NYou are very organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢井井有条的样子\NI like things tidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你在医院里的帮助\NThank you for helping me in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常勇敢\NThat was very courageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本能反应罢了\NIt's just reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"非常抱歉"\N"Very sorry".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常...\NVery...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\Nsorry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我有些幻觉\NI feel I'm having visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为头部创伤\NIt's the head trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一段时间内 你会无法依赖自己的意识\NYou won't be able to trust your own thoughts for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见一个瘟疫面具\NI saw a plague mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点像中世纪医生 ... 在黑死病肆虐时期的形象\NIt's the kind the medieval doctors wore in... during the Black death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲过类似的\NYou said something about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在出租车里讲过 不过大多不连贯\NYou were talking in the cab it was mostly incoherent but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的确听到"面具"两字\NBut I did hear the word mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有吗\NAnything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:16:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有躯体 血液 火焰 ...\NThe bodies, the blood and fire and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,... 和地狱\N... hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有位女士\NAnd there's a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位女士 她看着 ...\NThe woman, she seemed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 就必寻见\NSeek and find
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 看着很吓人\NUh. Well, seemed so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你肯定有人我们可以联系一下的\NNo, you got to have somebody we should call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有吗 为什么\NI do? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 ... 我有没有\NMy wat... Was I wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在去医院的时候戴着块手表\Nmy watch when I was brought to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没戴表\NYou weren't wearing a watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它对我意义重大 是我父母送的\NIt's important to me. It was a gift from my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你该朝前看 忘掉它\NLook, you should go ahead and clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的衣服沾血了 不过我想我有适合你穿的\NYour clothes are covered in blood but I think I got something that might fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿上后 我们就打电话给警方 行吗\NOnce you get dressed, we'll call the police, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 领事馆\NNo. No. The Consulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行 领事馆\NRight. The Consulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡\NCoffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.45,0:17:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入读伦敦国王学院的12岁神童\NProdidy, 12, to attend King's College
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳奇奥·布索尼 (昵称"小主教座堂")：我祈祷你一切安好\NIgnazio Busoni: I PRAY YOU ARE ALL RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳奇奥\NIgnazio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉无法依计划与你会面\NI'm sorry I couldn't meet as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们现在找上我了\NNow they're after me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所窃之物\NWhat we stole
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏于安全之所 本人亦是\N... is safely hidden, as am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所窃之物\N"What we stole"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天堂 25\NParadise Twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳奇奥\NIgnazio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的东西我都放浴室了\NI've left your things in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试这些\NTry these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁的\NWhose are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位朋友的\NA friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住这吗\NDoes he live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候\NSometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 有时候 蛤\NOh. Sometimes, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有点粗鲁了\NYou're being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不是那种人\NI'm sorry, I'm not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可说不准\NYou kind of are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在旧夹克里发现了这个\NI found this in my old jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是生物试管\NIt's a biotube.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用于运输危险物质\NThey're used for transporting dangerous substances.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用来干嘛\NWhat are you doing with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个高端装置\NIt's a high end unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,官方制造的\NGovernment issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿是指纹识别 万一遗失或被盗后的安保措施\NIt's called thumbprint recognition.\NSecurity in case it's lost or stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种管子只能由某位特定人物开启\NTubes like this can only be opened by a specified individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 人肯定不是我\NWell, it sure hell isn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那你为什么带着它 - 我不知道\N- Then why do you have it? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去查一下领事馆的号码\NI'm getting the number for the Consulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要 等等\NNo, please. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等过了 这样做不合适\NI have waited. This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会有它 你从哪儿弄的\NWhy do you have it? Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 有个简单的法子\NLook, there is a simple way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以弄清楚它究竟是不是我的\Nto find out if this thing belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去用拇指打开它 或者尝试失败\NThen my thumb will open it or it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开它 你疯了吗\NOpen it, are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果它是病毒药剂 我打开后它会被释放吗\NIf it's a viral agent, will it be released if I opened it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的 内部会有一层密封 甚至可能两层\NNo, there'll be an inner seal maybe even two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我自己交给别人之前 我想知道这是啥玩意\NBefore I put myself in anyone's hands I want to know what this thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还有我卷进了什么事件里面\NUh, and what I'm involved with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都合情合理 对吗\NThat make sense, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 达成一致\NSo, we agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把它打开\NWe're opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那说明它就是我的\NWell, that explains that it is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个象牙制成的密封圆柱体\NThis is a cylinder seal made of ivory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是骨头\NIt's bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人骨\NHuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三头带角的撒旦 正在吞噬三个人\NThree-headed, man eating Satan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中世纪时的常见形象\NA common image from the Middle Ages
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这与黑死病密切相连\Nassociated with the Black Plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三张血盆大口\NThe 3 gnashing mouths are symbolic of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是这瘟疫在人群中肆虐的象征\Nhow effectively the plague ate through the population.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你却记不起"咖啡"该怎么讲\NYet you can't remember the word for coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在一定程度上解释了我的幻觉\NIt explains my visions, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你听见了吗 - 嗯\N- Do you hear that? - Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是个法拉第指示器\NThis could be a Faraday pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.31,0:22:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为什么会这样 嗯\NSo why-why this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波提切利的画作 (文艺复兴早期的意大利佛罗伦萨画派艺术家)\NIt's Botticelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他的"地狱图"\NIt's his map of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细描绘了但丁笔下的地狱 (但丁 - 神曲·地狱篇)\NHe painted it as an illustration of Dante's Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻的时候我学习过但丁的作品\NI studied Dante when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是在幼儿园里\NProbably in kindergarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时挺着迷的\NI was a bit obsessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但丁定义了现代社会中的地狱概念\NDante defined our modern conception of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对地狱的看法700年前就定型了\NOur vision of it hasn't changed since he defined it 700 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波提切利画了出来 但 ... 但丁是众所周知的缔造者\NBotticelli drew it but... Dante created hell as we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是我的幻觉所见\NThis is what I have been seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.19,0:23:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷刑拷问 (图为地狱第八层：欺诈的献诈者)\NTorment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪孽亡魂 (图为地狱第八层：欺诈的挑拨离间者)\NSinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贩子被打上烙印 (图为地狱第八层：欺诈的神棍)\NBranding the mongers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎者全身发疹 (图为地狱第八层：欺诈的作伪者)\NLiars, covered with rashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.56,0:23:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预言者头部倒反 (图为地狱第八层：欺诈的占卜者)\NSoothsayers with their heads turned backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 蛇 - 对偷窃的刑罚 (图为地狱第八层：欺诈的盗贼)\N- Serpents. - The punishment for thievery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受难吧 罪人们 为汝之孽付出代价\NSuffer, you sinners. Pay for your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你对为何拥有此物一无所知\NSo you have no idea why you have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想现在或许该联系领事馆了\NI think maybe we call the consulate now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授\NProfessor Langdon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 是的 是我\NHello, yes. Speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地你还活着 我们一直在找你\NThank heavens you're alive. We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\NYou have?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还带着吗\NAre you still in possession?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登先生 管子还在吗\NMr. Langdon, do you have the tube?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 你的位置是\N- Yes. - Where are you located?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 我们找不着你 就无法帮你\NProfessor, we can't help you if we can't find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那是领事馆 他们又如何知情\NIf that's the consulate, how do they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们本就知道\NBecause they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.81,0:24:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办\NWhat do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.05,0:24:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们你在那儿\NTell them you're over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.05,0:24:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 教授 刚才断线了\N- Hello. - Professor, we were cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.05,0:24:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 抱歉\NYes, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.85,0:24:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿\NWhere are you located?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.05,0:24:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在一家旅馆里 佛罗伦萨家庭旅馆\NI'm at a hotel, Pensione la Fiorentina.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.79,0:24:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在房间里 我们的人马上就到\NStay in your room. We're sending someone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.42,0:24:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这等着 39号房\NI'll wait here, room 39.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.66,0:24:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我们就等着 看他们派谁来\NOkay. We wait and see who they send.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.30,0:24:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界卫生组织 流动指挥车\N清晨 6:37
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.29,0:24:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登通过佛罗伦萨的一个未加密IP登录了邮箱帐号\NLangdon accessed his email account from an unmasked IP address here in Florence
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.28,0:25:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么时候 - 7分钟前\N- When? - 7 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.28,0:25:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维亚多乐罗莎大道12号3C公寓\NVia Dolorosa, number 12, apartment 3C.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.32,0:25:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维亚多乐罗莎大道 要多久\NVia Dolorosa, how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.08,0:25:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12分钟\N12 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.03,0:25:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动 拿回指示器 还有兰登\NGo! I want that pointer back and I want Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.64,0:25:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 把他抓回来\NWhatever it takes, let's get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.28,0:25:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 走 走 走 就现在\NGo, go, go, go, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.96,0:25:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个 好奇怪\NLook at this. This is odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.05,0:25:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这块区域是但丁的地狱第八层\NThis area here is Dante's 8th level of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.72,0:25:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫Malebolge 意为邪恶之囊\NIt's called the Malebolge, means evil ditches.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.65,0:25:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一共有十种罪恶\NThere's ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.32,0:25:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿的字母"R" 原画中并没有\NThis letter "R" here, is not in the original painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.14,0:25:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是后加的\NIt's been added.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.38,0:25:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个\NThere's another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哪里 - 有个"E"\N- Where? - An "E".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.40,0:25:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被恶魔鞭笞的诱奸者\NOn seducers whipped by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.07,0:25:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 面颊上有个"C"的人 - 是污吏\N- There's a "C" on the cheek of a... - A grafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.55,0:25:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 贪污犯 - 困在满池沸腾沥青中的骗子\N- ... a grafter. - A conman trapped in a pool of boiling tar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.23,0:25:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- "V" "R" - 啊 那儿\N- A "V", "R".\N- Ah, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.03,0:25:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- "T" - 那儿 那儿 "A"\N- "T". - There, there, "A".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.75,0:25:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\NWhat is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.68,0:25:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一段文字 那是英文吗\NThat's text. Is that in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.62,0:26:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有透过死亡之眼 才能瞥见真相\NTHE TRUTH CAN BE GLIMPSED ONLY THROUGH THE EYES OF DEATH.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.20,0:26:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐布里斯特\NZOBRIST.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.89,0:26:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝特朗·佐布里斯特\NBertrand Zobrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.60,0:26:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 美国的亿万富翁 那一定很棒 - 蛤\N- American billionaire, that must be nice. - Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.81,0:26:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生物工程师\NBioengineer
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.63,0:26:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因激进观点而声名狼藉\NNotorious for radical views.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.75,0:26:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在这儿\NHere he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.15,0:26:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类经历了10万年\NIt took the earth's population a hundred thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.18,0:26:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才繁衍出10亿人口\Nto reach a billion people.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.55,0:26:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在随后的100年 人口增长到20亿\NAnd then just a hundred more to reach two billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.93,0:26:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再翻一番只花了50年 70年代人口40亿\NAnd only fifty years to double again to four billion people in 1970.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.33,0:26:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 我们快有80亿了\NWe're nearly at eight billion now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.45,0:26:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴特利特以烧杯为例 (巴特利特：英国化学家)\NBartlett used the example of a beaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.84,0:26:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内有一个细菌细胞\NWith a single bacterium.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.39,0:27:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每分钟分裂一次 数目翻倍\NOne that divides and doubles every minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.75,0:27:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在11点整将第一个细菌细胞置于杯中\NIf you placed the first bacterium into the beaker at 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.48,0:27:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12点整时杯就全满了\Nand it's completely full by 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.84,0:27:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在何时烧杯还是半满的呢\NAt what time is the beaker still only half full?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.79,0:27:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11:59
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.67,0:27:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是现在的我们\NThat's what time it is for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.00,0:27:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来40年内 会有320亿人口 在生死线上挣扎\NIn 40 years, 32 billion people... will fight to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.21,0:27:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没失败\NNo fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.03,0:27:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离午夜 我们还差一分钟\NWe're a minute to midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.44,0:27:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一次全球性的瘟疫灾难都可以被归咎于人口的过剩\NEvery single global ill that plagues the Earth can be traced back to human overpopulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.37,0:27:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而严肃的生育控制手段却毫无施行可能\NBut serious birth control measures they don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.87,0:27:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耸人听闻 违背个人权利\NOutrageous! Violation of my rights!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.93,0:27:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵犯个人隐私 别来好为人师\NInvasion of my privacy! Don't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.32,0:27:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 我们仍在侵略自然环境\NBut still we keep attacking our own environment!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.51,0:28:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球历史上已经有过5次物种大灭绝\NThey have been 5 major extinctions in the earth's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.50,0:28:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们若不立即采取大胆行动\NUnless we take bold immediate action
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.50,0:28:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六次就会轮到我们头上\Nthe sixth extinction will be our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.64,0:28:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离午夜 我们还差一分钟\NWe're a minute to midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.25,0:28:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来他有挺多拥护者\NLooks like he's got a lot of followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.22,0:28:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 来自全球各地 五湖四海\NYeah, from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.68,0:28:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他挺令人信服的\NHe is compelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.27,0:28:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在佐布里斯特消失的两年时间里 部分当局人员担心\NThe 2 year disappearance during which some authorities feared Zobrist
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.44,0:28:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能研发了一种有害于免疫能力底下群体的病毒病原体\Nmay have designed an opportunistic viral pathogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.70,0:28:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他制造了一种瘟疫病毒\NHe created a plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.86,0:28:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 为什么是但丁\NBut, why Dante?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.63,0:28:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是这幅"地狱图"\NWhy this map of hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.20,0:28:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是拼图游戏 或者挑战吗\NIs this supposed to be a puzzle or a challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.19,0:28:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是遗书\NOr a suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.07,0:28:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3天前他自杀了\NHe killed himself 3 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.85,0:29:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等级\NThe levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.02,0:29:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪恶等级是乱序的 这是困扰我的地方\NThe levels are out of order, that's what's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.25,0:29:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱这一层的次序被重新分布了\NThis circles of hell had been rearranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.48,0:29:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟医院的女子是同一人\NIt's the same woman from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.03,0:29:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能待在这 肯定不能相信领事馆了\NWe can't stay here. We certainly can't trust the Consulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.48,0:29:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字母像布置时那样被加密 也不对\NThe letters are encrypted as committers, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.59,0:29:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果病毒真的存在 你知道有多少政府想要弄到手吗\NIf the plague exist, do you know how many governments would want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.05,0:29:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神棍 猜不出\NClerical profiteers, not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.75,0:29:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他们都会做些什么来得到这些 - 挑拨离间者 不是\N- What they would do to get it. - Someone who discord dead, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.89,0:29:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生化武器\NA biological weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.43,0:29:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些字母\NThe letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.98,0:29:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把每种罪行都加上了字母 然后打乱次序\NHe has assigned a letter to each sin and then changed their order.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.23,0:29:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他设了一个字谜\NHe's made an anagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.44,0:29:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 字谜\NYes. Anagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.53,0:29:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 我知道另一条路能出去\NLet's go. I know another way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.14,0:30:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你带了手机 最好留在这儿\NIf you have phoned, best leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.64,0:30:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会被追踪\NThey might track it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.95,0:30:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机 衣服都不是我自个的\NThe phone? I'm not even wearing my own clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.66,0:30:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 走吧\NGood. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.15,0:30:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特·兰登 世界卫生组织\NRobert Langdon! World Health Organization! (WHO)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.35,0:30:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V, R, O.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.91,0:30:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得重排这些字母 Over Code\NI got to rearrange these letters, CATROVACER.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.05,0:30:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Covered Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.12,0:30:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天 这种东西我以前挺上手的\NGod. I used to be good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.40,0:30:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cerca trova.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.95,0:30:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意大利语 意为"寻找"和"发现"\NIt's Italian. It means "seek" and "find".
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.91,0:30:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cerca trova 好的\NCerca trova. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.80,0:30:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我为什么会在佛罗伦萨了\NI know why I am in Florence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.97,0:31:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界卫生组织已经抵达 待命\NWorld Health Organization has landed, standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.30,0:31:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意\NBe advised.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.38,0:31:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自巴黎的布沙尔探员已经到场\NAgent Bouchard, from the Paris office is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.88,0:31:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界卫生组织 告诉我最新情况\NW.H.O, Bring me up to speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.10,0:31:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布沙尔已经上去了\NBouchard is up there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.98,0:31:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们去哪 - 旧宫 波波利花园附近\N- Where are we going? - The Palazzo Vecchio, near the Boboli Gardens.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.04,0:32:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发现他\NThere's no sign of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.39,0:32:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布沙尔说兰登已经走了 指示器也不在\NBouchard says Langdon is gone and so is the pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.94,0:32:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行\NWell, I need better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.33,0:32:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你 你们全部都要表现得更好\NI need better from you, from you, from all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.57,0:32:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更像样\NBetter!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.96,0:32:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要更迅速 更敏捷 别相信任何人\NWork faster. Work smarter. Don't trust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.93,0:32:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家加油吧\NLet's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.53,0:32:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 去吧 - 是\N- Let's go. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.40,0:32:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报看样子已经没用了\NThe information seems to be obsolete.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.80,0:32:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不要透露给秘书长 明白吗 - 明白\N- Do not say anything to the secretary general. - OK
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.08,0:32:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 身份 - 瓦任莎\N- Identification. - Vayentha.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.85,0:32:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 继续 - 我要跟教务长通话\N- Go ahead. - I need to speak to the provost.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.03,0:32:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.80,0:32:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚得里亚海 (意大利东部地中海水域) 清晨 7:12\N游艇"门达西乌姆号"\NAdriatic Sea 7:12 AM\NThe Mendacium.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.52,0:33:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 WHO在追踪兰登这事上先你一步 瓦任莎\NSo, the WHO beat you to Mr. Langdon, Vayentha.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.93,0:33:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教务长可不喜欢这样\NThe provost isn't going to like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.50,0:33:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 他想要清掉我了\NI know. He's going to want to liquidate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.07,0:33:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他这儿不是柏林\NTell him this isn't Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.68,0:33:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他敢试 我就找上门\NHe tries anything and I will find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.94,0:33:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小时内再试一遍 然后联系我们\NTry to reacquire and make contact in 60 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.10,0:33:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有在听 我不是一次性用品\NDid you hear me? I am not disposable.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.45,0:33:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦任莎 抢先将法拉第指示器弄到手\NVayentha, get the Faraday pointer before the government does.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.68,0:33:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠\NShit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.96,0:33:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 西姆斯先生 - 嗯\N- Mr. Sims. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.56,0:33:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情出了点偏差\NThere's been a deviation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.90,0:33:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到这个真遗憾\NSorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.14,0:33:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么行动 - 佛罗伦萨\N- What operation? - Florence.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.33,0:33:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的新外勤似乎有点随性乱来了\NOur new players seemed to have gone off script.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.49,0:33:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够业余\NHow unprofessional.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.42,0:34:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在WHO已经取代了我们的位置\NAnd now the WHO has overtaken our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.01,0:34:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉瓦任莎 如果她还在乎这份工作\NTell Vayentha, if she values her position
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.91,0:34:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就该除掉兰登\Nshe will remove Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.71,0:34:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁尸灭迹\NBody not found.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.86,0:34:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者再妙点 拦路抢劫\NOr better yet, a mugging gone awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.42,0:34:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来上一刀 我觉得 现金劫走 钱包留下\NA blade, I think. Cash gone, wallet remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.15,0:34:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧确认下 然后继续 继续 继续\NLet's have a quick identification and move on. Move on, move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.28,0:34:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授已经脱离监视了\NProfessor Langdon is out of frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.28,0:34:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还带着管子吗 - 是的\N- And in possession of the tube? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.37,0:34:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他带着法拉第指示器\NHe has the Faraday pointer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.48,0:34:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前盯的那么紧\NHe was such a good frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.38,0:34:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 瓦任莎的情况如何 - 无恙 但很焦虑\N- What is Vayentha's condition? - Intact but anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.81,0:34:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也正常\NShe should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.48,0:35:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位委托人究竟都让我们做了些什么\NWhat in god's name has this client gotten us into?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.02,0:35:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 只是个 ... 比方\NNo, no, no. This is uh... rhetorical.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.96,0:35:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么时候准备好发布委托人的视频\NWhen are we due to release the client's video?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.30,0:35:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视频刚到这\NIt just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.51,0:35:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的指示是24小时内上传\NHis instructions were to upload it in 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.89,0:35:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在想看一下\NI want to look at it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.50,0:35:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 委托人 佐布里斯特\NBut, the client, Mr. Zobrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.98,0:35:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,委托人 委托人已经死了 我要看视频\NThe client, the client is dead. I want to see the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.33,0:35:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是违约行为\NThat's a violation of our protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.99,0:35:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是政府 只是负责办事\NWe're not the government. We get things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.32,0:35:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿博加斯特先生\NMr. Arbogast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.23,0:35:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够令我们在工作中得心应手的首要因素\NChief among the attributes that makes us so very good at our job
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.42,0:35:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是世人对我们存在的一无所知\Nis that as far as the world is concerned, we don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.15,0:35:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若这段视频暗示或甚至提及到我们\NIf this video implicates or even mentions us in anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.93,0:35:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会基于客户权益考虑而中止其发布\NI want to stop it's release. For the benefit of all our clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.64,0:35:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要求过在流程操作中要避免异常事况 就这些\NYou asked me to avoid abnormalities in procedure, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.46,0:35:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果佐布里斯特先生当初只是在假装正常交易 怎么办\NWhat about Mr. Zobrist has ever remotely resembled normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.74,0:36:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那 我... - 也只是个比方\N- Well, I... - Also rhetorical.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.58,0:36:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把视频带过来\NBring me the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.80,0:36:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旧宫(维奇奥宫)的五百人大厅内 有一副著名壁画\N马基雅维利大道 佛罗伦萨 意大利 上午 8:36\NIn the Vecchio's Hall of the Five Hundred, there's a famous mural,\NViale Machiavelli, Florence, Italy 8:36 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.89,0:36:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔治奥·瓦萨里的"马西阿诺之战"\NGiorgio Vasari's Battle of Marciano.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.38,0:36:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在壁画顶部附近 有一段密文\NNear the top of the mural is a coded message
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.32,0:36:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是艺术界中最著名的未解之谜\Nwhich is one the art world's most famous puzzles.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.14,0:36:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密文是什么\NAnd what's the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.54,0:36:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cerca trova.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.93,0:36:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 就寻见\NSeek and find.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.78,0:36:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在医院里 我一直念叨说我很抱歉\NAt the hospital, I kept saying I was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.91,0:36:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 一遍又一遍\NVery sorry, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 也许那不是我的本意\NWell, maybe that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.90,0:36:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画家的名字 瓦萨里 我可能讲的是"瓦萨里"\NThe name of the artist, Vasari. I could have been saying Vasari.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.61,0:36:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒啊 感觉你清醒多了\NThat's good. You seem clearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.75,0:36:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 你的中间名叫什么\N- I am. - What's your middle name?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.52,0:36:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我挺清醒的\NWell, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.68,0:36:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NMm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.36,0:36:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐布里斯特死了 但若病毒真的存在\NZobrist is dead but if his plague is real...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.31,0:36:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这幅"地狱图" 就是他留给某人找到它的线索\NThen this map is a trail he has left so someone can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.27,0:36:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.78,0:36:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 跟他立场一致的人\NWell, someone who believes the same as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.72,0:36:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你带着它的原因\NAnd that's why you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.10,0:36:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我印象中从未见过他\NWell, I don't remember ever meeting Zobrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.74,0:36:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不记得的事情可多了\NThere's a lot you don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.08,0:37:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他们 也许他们之前找到你\NMaybe they- Maybe they came to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.27,0:37:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征求过你的指引\NWanted your help with the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.91,0:37:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就因为我做过但丁的讲座 - 正是如此\N- Because I lectured on Dante? - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.90,0:37:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们向你展示法拉第指示器 试着说服你支持那些主张\NThey showed you this Faraday pointer, tried to convince you of their cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.17,0:37:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 大屠杀 - 你说过他挺令人信服的\N- Mass murder? - You said you found him compelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.75,0:37:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是指观点\NHis argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.34,0:37:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口才\NHis rhetoric.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.11,0:37:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝非这些计划 佐布里斯特心理上有问题\NNot his plan! Zobrist is a psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.38,0:37:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 或许他们耍了你\NWell, maybe they tricked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.92,0:37:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实给了 ... 你认识的人\NSent... someone you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.90,0:37:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离午夜还差一分钟\NIt's a minute to midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.13,0:37:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那是对付咱们的吗 - 常理来看是的\N- Is that for us? - Logic would suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.58,0:37:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.91,0:37:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿 快 跟上我\NHere, come on. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.97,0:37:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以穿过花园到那儿\NWe could get there through the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.09,0:38:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 旧宫在这边\NOkay, the- the Palazzo Vecchio is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.11,0:38:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去一小时内 我们标记了她用信用卡购买的汽车\NWe just flagged the car charged to her credit card within the past hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.75,0:38:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安托万 你跟警方交涉了么\NAntoine, did you talk to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.56,0:38:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有见过咱们的警察\NThere are people who have seen me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.62,0:38:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟当地警方合作\NPlease cooperate with local police officially.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.10,0:38:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WHO将负责监督波波利花园的搜查工作\NW.H.O. will take charge overseeing the search at the Boboli Gardens.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.28,0:38:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把搜查犬调过来\NCall in the search dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.70,0:38:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在警局里接到电话 前来支援你\NI got called out from the police station to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.30,0:38:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波波利花园 上午 8:42\NBoboli Gardens 8:42 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.08,0:38:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要更多帮手\NI need more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.51,0:39:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告电台 发现嫌犯\NRadio in, suspects found.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.01,0:39:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的 四组 检查北边\NDamn it! Delta, check the north perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.69,0:39:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿下去有扇灰色的小门\NThere's a small gray door down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.46,0:39:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直通瓦萨里长廊\NIt will take us into the Vasari corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.57,0:39:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过维奇奥桥 就进到了宫里\NRight across the Ponte Vecchio, and into the Palazzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.55,0:39:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 门在那 看 - 哦\N- That's the door, see. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.20,0:39:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.97,0:39:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花园是不是被墙整个围住的\NIs the garden completely walled.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.75,0:40:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四面全封闭\NOn all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.12,0:40:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的出口要穿过北面的碧提宫\NThe only exits are through the Palazzo Pitti, on the north side,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.26,0:40:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者通过东西两侧接待游客的大门\Nand through the visitors gates on the east and west sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.90,0:40:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有别的出路了\NNo other way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.01,0:40:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果瓦萨里长廊大门也算的话\NI suppose if you count the Vasari gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.17,0:40:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那门很老 鲜有人知\NBut it's ancient, no one knows about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.77,0:40:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登知道\NLangdon does.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.66,0:40:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授现在是个麻烦了 瓦任莎\NThe Professor has become a liability, Vayentha.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.52,0:40:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教务长已经发布了诛杀令 除掉兰登\NThe provost has issued a kill order. Eliminate Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.10,0:40:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如若失败 你要负责 我说得够清楚了吗\NFail, and you will be held accountable. Am I making myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.58,0:40:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 长官\NCopy that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.90,0:40:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧宫五百人大厅 早上 9:13
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.29,0:40:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.37,0:40:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦萨里的壁画 马西阿诺之战\NThat's the Vasari fresco, The Battle of Marciano.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.50,0:41:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿 那儿 看 看 看 看\NThere. There. Look. Look, look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.18,0:41:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 看那两栋农舍 壁画中间往上\NOkay, see the 2 farmhouses, dead center up high,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.09,0:41:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往4点钟方向下移一点\Ncome down to it's 4 o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.84,0:41:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就看到一小面绿色战旗\Nand you'll see a small green flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.47,0:41:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Cerca trova - 对\N- Cerca trova. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.59,0:41:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 就寻见\NSeek and find.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.90,0:41:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 就寻见\NSeek and find.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.77,0:41:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们看到了 找到了\NWe sought it and we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.28,0:42:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 现在做什么\NSo, now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.36,0:42:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐布里斯特加到画里的话\NThe words Zobrist added to the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.66,0:42:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有透过死亡之眼 才能瞥见真相\NThe truth can be glimpsed only through the eyes of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.74,0:42:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡之眼\NEyes of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.77,0:42:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁的眼睛\NWhose's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.75,0:42:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是被注射了什么东西\NWas I given an injection?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.74,0:42:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候\NWhen?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.64,0:42:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 医院里面 颈动脉注射 - 没有\N- At the hospital, with a hypertenol? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.28,0:43:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 你是插管输液治疗 只有静脉滴注\NNo, you were intubated. Anything you got came through the IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.19,0:43:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在医院里\NNot at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.55,0:43:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时身着正装 在车厢后座上\NI was fully dress. I was in the back of some car...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.92,0:43:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是过去两天里的某个时候\Nat some point in the last 2 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.20,0:43:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西注入了我的血液里\NAnd something was injected into my bloodstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.62,0:43:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后现在我开始外现临床病状\Nand now I'm showing signs of an illness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.11,0:43:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是...\NWhat if...?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.16,0:43:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是什么\NWhat if what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.95,0:43:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西恩娜 我会不会就是携带者\NSienna, what if I'm the carrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.89,0:43:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.35,0:43:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你携带了 那我也会被感染\NIf you've got it then I've got it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.97,0:43:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我们接触过的每个人同样如此 都会死掉\NAnd everyone we've come into contact with has it and will likely die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.82,0:43:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果并非如此\NBut if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.04,0:43:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 如果他们注射的是药剂或致幻剂 或者别的东西\NIf-If they gave you an anotic or a hallucinogen or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.96,0:43:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们仍有机会挽救这半个世界\NThen we still have a chance to save half the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.50,0:43:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得一试 不是么\NIt's worth a try, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.60,0:44:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\NProfessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.40,0:44:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是你 你怎么这么快就回来了\NAh, it is you. Why are you back so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.98,0:44:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道她是谁\NI have no idea who this woman is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.47,0:44:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这身行头我差点没认出来 在逛街吗\NI almost didn't recognize you in that suit. You've been shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.84,0:44:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 你的头被撞了\NProfessor, you bumped your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.15,0:44:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 洗澡的时候 暴跌一跤\NIn the shower, yes. It's quite a tumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.99,0:44:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哎呀 - 嗯\N- Ayes. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.03,0:44:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下 这位是西恩娜 我的侄女\NI'm sorry. This is Sienna, my niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.13,0:44:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你人在意大利呢 教授 不必提这个\NYou're in Italy, Professor, you don't have to say 'niece'.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.96,0:44:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不是 不是的 - 不是的 他没有\N- No. No. - No, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.46,0:44:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 玛塔·阿尔瓦雷兹 很高兴见到你\NHello. Marta Alvarez. Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.01,0:44:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳奇奥(小主教座堂)也跟你一块来了吗\NIs Ignazio with you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.83,0:44:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 伊格纳奇奥 - 对\N- Ignazio? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.09,0:44:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳奇奥今早没能成行\NIgnazio couldn't make it this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.90,0:44:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉打搅你一下 玛塔 不过\NI'm sorry to bother you, Marta. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.03,0:45:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你大概能想到我为什么会在这里 又一次\NI can imagine you know why I'm back. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.00,0:45:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.85,0:45:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧宫里头这么多的珍宝\NOf all the treasures in the Palazzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.80,0:45:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上他跟小主教座堂在那上面待了将近一个钟头\NHe and il Duomino spent almost an hour with it up there last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.31,0:45:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 非同寻常\NIt's-It's so morbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.27,0:45:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里 这很正常\NNo. No. It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.57,0:45:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 来吧 我来带路\NAlright, come on. I'm headed up that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.09,0:45:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真是足智多谋的一个能人\NHe's an extremely resourceful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.34,0:45:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也对你说过这话 布沙尔先生\NI was told you were as well, Mr. Bouchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.72,0:45:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 告诉我\NSo. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.96,0:45:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他在干嘛\NWhat do you think he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.42,0:45:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你在干嘛\NWhat you think you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.83,0:45:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把指示器带给你 现在它没了\NI brought you the pointer and now it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.05,0:45:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你弄丢了 - 我们在街上跟丢了他\N- You have a leak. - We losed him in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.28,0:45:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在医生的住处又重新发现了\NReacquired him at the doctor's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.30,0:45:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大家支持 我还能掌控\NI can handle with some ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.02,0:45:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们不需要你帮忙 - 如果他受伤了\N- We don't need your help. - What if he's injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.94,0:45:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头部受创\NA head wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.92,0:45:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思 你认为他糊涂了\NWhat? You think he's confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.30,0:46:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他不知道他在干嘛吗 - 有可能\N- He doesn't know what he's doing? - It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.91,0:46:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他晚上失踪前进展到了哪里\NHow far did he get the night before he disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.45,0:46:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五百人大厅\NTo the Hall of Five Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.11,0:46:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就不追了\NSo let's stop chasing him,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.61,0:46:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提前守着他\Nanticipate him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.86,0:46:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 朋友 还请悠着点\NWhoa, inspector. Not so fast, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.10,0:46:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快燃起来了\NI'm about to burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.24,0:46:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么浪漫的一天 他却带你来欣赏死亡面具\NSuch a romantic date he takes you on. To see a death mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.48,0:46:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 在16世纪 它们相当普遍\NYeah, they were common practice in the 1500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.20,0:46:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实质上就是某个人面部的石膏模型\NIt's essentially just a plaster cast of someone's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.18,0:46:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其死后不久套模浇注的\Nmade a few moments after that person dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.76,0:46:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"透过死亡之眼"\N"Through the eyes of death."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.40,0:46:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这幅面具的模型 是一位诗人\NThe person who was used for this mask, the poet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.80,0:46:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫但丁\NDante.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.04,0:46:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这是一个浪漫的故事\NIt is a romantic story I supposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.60,0:47:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但丁热爱这座城市 他在当时很显赫 又有影响力 但\NDante loved Florence, he was prominent and powerful. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.58,0:47:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在政治权力更迭后 他被罢黜流放\NThe political winds changed and he was exiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.48,0:47:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们威胁他 若胆敢回来 就火刑伺候\NThey threatened to burn him at the stake if he ever returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.77,0:47:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上 有人认为对但丁的放逐 是面具看着如此悲恸的原因\NActually, some people say Dante's exile is the reason his death mask looks so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.98,0:47:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不对 那是因为比阿特丽斯的原因 ("神曲"中的人物)\NNo. No. It was because of Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.09,0:47:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但丁只从远处见过她 但她却被其终生迷恋\NDante only knew her from afar but he was obsessed with her his entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.87,0:47:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的侄女很浪漫呢 教授\NYour niece is a romantic, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.15,0:47:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们认为 但丁所撰的穿越地狱之行 实际上是为了找到她\NThey say Dante wrote in fact about his journey out of hell to reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.14,0:47:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他没能成功\NBut he never made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.82,0:47:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已嫁给另主\NShe married someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.21,0:47:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事常常发生\NThat happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.15,0:47:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗\NDoes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.88,0:47:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁撇下了谁\NWho left who?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些东西 若你不加以照料 就会难以为继\NThings fall apart if you don't look after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.60,0:47:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 馆方要求 参观时你们只能站在立柱外\NOh. We ask that you stay behind the stanchions. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.09,0:47:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.96,0:47:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得很巧 教授 我们刚刚开门\NGood timing, Professor. We've only just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.71,0:47:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛塔...\NMarta...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.92,0:47:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.55,0:48:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿 那是我们\NThere. That's us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.16,0:48:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是伊格纳奇奥·布索尼 ("小主教座堂")\NThat's Ignazio Busoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.47,0:48:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们相识多年\NI've known him for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.88,0:48:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是研究但丁的学者\NHe's the Dante scholar.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.86,0:48:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面具的主人坚持要求参观者要站在立柱之外\NThe mask's owner insists on the stanchions to keep people back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.03,0:48:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未经许可 工作人员也不能打开展柜\NHe doesn't even permit staff to open the case without him present.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.29,0:48:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以面具不是博物馆所有\NSo the mask is not owned by the museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.21,0:48:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 有位私人收藏家从我们手里买下了\NNo. A private collector bought it from us,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.26,0:49:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并允许我们做永久性展览\Nand allows us to display it in perpetuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.61,0:49:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是筹集经费的惯常做法\NIt's a common practice, to raise funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.90,0:49:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是何许人也\NWho is the collector?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.18,0:49:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝特朗·佐布里斯特 那位亿万富翁\NBertram Zobrist, the billionaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.68,0:49:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的观点很古怪 但其自杀之事仍旧令人遗憾\NHis ideas were quite eccentric, but still it's such a shame what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.64,0:49:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我接电话的时候了\NThat's when I got the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.00,0:49:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.53,0:49:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 我 我不知道该作何感想\NProfessor, I... I don't know what to think!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.73,0:49:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很震惊\NI am appalled!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.67,0:50:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 教授 - 兰登教授\N- Professor. - Professor Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.09,0:50:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 这事情肯定有个解释\NLook. There's an explanation for all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.84,0:50:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察来了 警铃响了\NThe police came and the alarm went off.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.10,0:50:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是什么人\NWho are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.35,0:50:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都是特工人员\NThey're government agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.98,0:50:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有客人了\NYou have an intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.77,0:50:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上回来\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.00,0:50:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛塔 别让他俩跑了\NMarta, don't let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.75,0:50:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能带枪进这来\NYou can not bring a gun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.12,0:50:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\NProfessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.69,0:50:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 我非常尊敬您 但我不明白\NProfessor, I very much respect you but I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.63,0:50:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 请坐 我会解释 - 你为什么做这事\N- Please sit down. I'm going to explain this. - Why you have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.82,0:50:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那可不行 - 玛塔 我不知道面具在哪儿\N- This is not okay. - Marta, I do not know where the mask is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.65,0:50:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我会竭尽全力找到它 还给你们\NBut I will do everything I can to find it and return it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.42,0:51:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 你在干嘛 教授 求你 不要\NProfessor, what are you doing? Professor, please. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.41,0:51:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 回来 别这样\NProfessor, come back. Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.90,0:51:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 请不要\NProfessor, please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.30,0:51:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嘿 嘿 - 教授\N- Hey. Hey. - Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.42,0:51:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你别跟着就好 - 求你了 别这样\N- Just don't follow us. - Please, don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.52,0:51:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\NProfessor!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.28,0:51:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们偷偷找条路子离开这儿\NLet's just calmly find a way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.03,0:51:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不告诉我伊格纳奇奥的事情\NWhy didn't you tell me about Ignazio?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.04,0:51:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你知道我是个贼 你还会帮我吗\NWould you help me if you knew I was a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.41,0:51:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向我求助的时候撒了谎\NYou lied to me when you asked for my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.04,0:51:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 严格说来 我有所保留\NWell technically, I withheld.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.72,0:51:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我真的拿了那副面具...\NIf I really took that mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.18,0:51:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的确拿了 我刚刚才看到\NYou did take the mask, I just saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.82,0:51:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你的问题 你不必跟着\NThis is not your problem. You don't have to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.46,0:51:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然要陪着 人类正面临生死存亡\NOf course, I do. Human lives are at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.69,0:51:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想知道我没站错队\NI just want to know that I'm on the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.45,0:51:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有\NYou are.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.45,0:51:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓\NI swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.24,0:51:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.01,0:52:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在咱们去找到要找的东西\NNow let's find what we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.69,0:52:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打给伊格纳奇奥 问他面具藏哪儿了\NCall this Ignazio, and ask him where he hid the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.91,0:52:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格纳奇奥失踪了 不知藏身何处\NIgnazio's disappeared. He had gone into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.00,0:52:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说过\NHe said.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.04,0:52:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人也在追着他 但他留了条线索\NThey were chasing him too but he left a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.62,0:52:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一封邮件 "天堂 25"\NAn email, "Paradise Twenty-five".
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.43,0:52:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指的是但丁"神曲"中的天堂篇第25诗章 不过\NThat's a reference to Dante's Divine Comedy. "Canto XXV." But...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.88,0:52:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我现在需要那本书 - 一本书\N- I need a copy of the book. - A copy of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.52,0:52:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真荒诞 我会用谷歌\NThat's quaint. I use Google.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.61,0:52:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正在关闭博物馆 只开放主出口\NThey're closing down the museum, only the main exit is going to be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.33,0:52:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就穿过亚美尼亚\NWell, then we'll go through Armenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.30,0:52:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...从正门有序离开\N...Go out to the front door in an orderly manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.21,0:53:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现已封锁全部出口\NAll exit doors are now sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.10,0:53:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是唯一的进出通道\NThis is the only way in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.91,0:53:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有隐藏的出口 隧道 隐门之类的\NWhat about hidden exits? Tunnels, concealed doorways?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.33,0:53:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方700年了 先生 这类玩意很多\NIt's a 700 year old Palazzo, Signore, there are a number of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.27,0:53:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我看看\NShow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.78,0:53:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚美尼亚\NARMENIA
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.74,0:53:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 真是刮目相看\NProfessor. How worldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.08,0:53:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧宫的秘密之一\NSecrets of the Palazzo Invisibile.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.78,0:53:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段路很赞 改天你也试试\NIt's a great tour, you should take it sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.17,0:53:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这儿暂时安全了\NWe should be safe here for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.46,0:54:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.93,0:54:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"到那时 我将带着另一个声音 另一身羊毛..."\N"By then with other voice, with other fleece..."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.19,0:54:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我将作为诗人回归 并且\N在我的洗礼盆中接受那花冠..."\N"I shall return as poet and put on,\Nat my baptismal font, the laurel crown..."
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.91,0:54:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗礼盆\NBaptismal font.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.97,0:54:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母百花大教堂 但丁受洗之地\N(译注: Il Duomo实指佛罗伦萨主教座堂广场建筑群 包括圣母百花大教堂 圣若望洗礼堂 乔托钟楼等)\NIl Duomo. The Cathedral where Dante was baptized.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.71,0:54:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是伊格纳奇奥工作的地方 他把面具藏在那了\NThat's where Ignazio works. That's where he hid the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.80,0:54:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在这儿\NIt is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.18,0:54:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会认为我们正前往出口\NThey're going to think we're heading down to the exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.63,0:54:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们往上走\NThen we go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.04,0:54:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.56,0:54:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在五百人大厅上面\NWe're right above the Hall of Five Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.06,0:54:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一头有道楼梯 直通大街\NThere's a stairway leading down to the street on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.29,0:54:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\NSo.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.07,0:55:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次迈一步\NOne step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.90,0:55:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吗\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.30,0:55:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你恐高不\NAre you afraid of heights?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.54,0:55:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点儿\NA little.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.82,0:55:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是有点儿幽闭恐惧症\NI'm uncomfortable in tight spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.73,0:55:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 别往下看\NSo, don't look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.59,0:55:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者就往下看 我记不得了\NOr do. I can never remember which.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.74,0:56:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么难\NIt's not that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.35,0:56:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 走\NCome on, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.36,0:56:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西恩娜\NSienna!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.87,0:56:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NAre you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.61,0:56:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗 - 还好\N- You okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.28,0:56:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 只要... 慢慢去到那边横梁上\NAlright, just... crawl along that beam there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.45,0:56:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在另一边跟你碰头 楼梯附近\NAnd I'll meet you on the far side, by the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.52,0:56:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.86,0:56:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调派六个人到这来 不用戒备了\NGive me a six men stationed here. Safeties off.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.60,0:57:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在变蠢了 兰登教授\NYou're being stupid now, Professor Langdon!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.26,0:57:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 走 离开这儿 走\NGo. Go. Get out of here, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.60,0:57:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一度需要你 但如今心意已改\NThey needed you but now they changed their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.81,0:57:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把人都赶走 大家都离开 清空现场\NGet these people out. Everyone out, clear the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.18,0:58:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它给我\NGive me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.05,0:58:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些门 这儿\NThese doors, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.27,0:58:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 东面 他们去那了 - 收到\N- Eastern side. That's where they're headed. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.88,0:58:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 行动 快点\NGo, move. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.25,0:59:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布沙尔 布沙尔探员 回话\NBouchard. Agent Bouchard, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.89,0:59:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿 布沙尔探员 回话\NWhat is your location? Agent Bouchard, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.07,0:59:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重生\N<font color="#ff8080">REBIRTH</font>
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.02,0:59:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄来视频的信封上也有这个词\NThat same word is on the envelope the video arrived in,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.61,0:59:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面还有一个日期 是明天\Nalong with the date. The date is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.70,0:59:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 这些我知道\NWell, thank you, that was not lost on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.64,0:59:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱中最黑暗的地方 是为那些\NThe darkest places in hell are reserved for those
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.71,0:59:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在道德危机时刻皂白不辨的人而准备的\Nwho refuse to act in time of moral crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.33,0:59:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但丁的地狱并非虚构 它是预言\NDante's hell isn't fiction anymore, it's prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.97,0:59:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经在这个星球上打造了人间地狱\NWe have created our own hell on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.30,0:59:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\NOh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.09,0:59:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告已然很明显 对策却被忽略了\NThe warnings have been obvious, the solutions ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.39,0:59:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我采取了行动\NSo, I took action.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.91,0:59:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你看到了这则视频 就意味着地狱病毒\NIf you are watching this, it means the Inferno virus was released
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.12,0:59:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已在昨晚午夜被释放\Nlast night at midnight, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.54,1:00:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在早就传遍了全球各个角落\Nit's now being carried to every corner of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.45,1:00:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\NOh my.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.27,1:00:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在释放后的6天内 病毒会不断增殖 (译注: 上帝创造天地用时6天)\NWithin 6 days of it's released, the virus will replicate itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.70,1:00:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球上的全体人类数量\NAnd every man, woman and child on Earth expect the current...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.44,1:00:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会随机减半\Nthe current population to be culled by half.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.70,1:00:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸存者则将见证\NThe survivors will witness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.97,1:00:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星球上前所未有的恐怖\Nhorrors... unknown to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.71,1:00:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想让大家知道原由\NBut I want them to know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.39,1:00:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是吾之所为 这就是吾之救赎\NThat this was our doing and this is our salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.26,1:00:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在时候已到\NNow is the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.75,1:00:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是...\NToday is...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.66,1:00:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面还有\NThere's more.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.71,1:00:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信我已经明白了视频主旨\NI believe I've got the gist.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.44,1:00:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显过去数年以来\NIt appears our organization has spent
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.20,1:00:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在跟一个试图通过自行研发的致命病毒\Nthe last several years in the employ of a madman
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.05,1:00:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来发动人口大屠杀的疯子在打交道\Nwho now intends to commit a mass murder using a deadly plague of his own creation
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.72,1:00:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在接下来24小时的某一刻 ... 抱歉\Nin some point in the next 24... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.05,1:00:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到12小时了\NLess than 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.51,1:01:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 咱们尽吾所能 不要再\NSo, let's do our level best not to fuck things up
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.41,1:01:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把事儿进一步搞砸了 好吗\Nany worse than we already have, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.86,1:01:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了法拉第指示器 没人能找到病毒\NWithout the Faraday pointer, no one can find the virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.53,1:01:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授现在在哪\NWhere is Professor Langdon now?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.13,1:01:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他之前跟布鲁克斯医生在波波利花园 但情报似乎断了\NHe was with Dr. Brooks in the Boboli Gardens but we seemed to have lost visual.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.82,1:01:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们恐怕也有很久没有联系上瓦任莎了\NAnd I'm afraid we have no contact from Vayentha.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.51,1:01:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.59,1:01:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲自去佛罗伦萨\NI'm going to Florence myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.94,1:01:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她做传染性检查 把这里隔离起来\NTest her for signs of contagion and quarantine this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.24,1:01:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不尽快找到兰登\NIf we don't find Langdon very soon,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.08,1:01:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很快就会看到更多死尸\Nwe are going to be looking at a great many more dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.23,1:02:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NAre you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.08,1:02:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚弱\NIt's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.12,1:02:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是虚弱 该死的\NJust weakness, god damn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.60,1:02:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们歇一会儿\NWe'll just take a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.47,1:02:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到她掉下去了吗\NDid you see her down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.40,1:02:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.43,1:02:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自打我11岁开始 全部所做所学\NEverything I've done, every bit of work and studies since I was eleven
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.61,1:02:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是去救死扶伤 而不是置人死地\Nis to stop death, not cause it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.62,1:02:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是自卫 有人要刺杀咱们\NIt was self defense. Someone was trying to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.71,1:02:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道能不能跟下去了\NI don't know if I can finish this.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.03,1:02:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能的话 我完全理解\NI understand if you can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.37,1:02:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 佐布里斯特才是谋杀犯 不是你\NLook, Zobrist is the murderer, not you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.34,1:02:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了我\NYou saved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.83,1:02:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本不必采取行动的\NYou don't have to take another step.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.59,1:02:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说的没错\NYeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.36,1:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了应该做的 若有必要 我还会再来一遍\NI did what was necessary and I'll do it again if I need to.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.55,1:02:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我祈愿这是最后一次\NI pray that you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.71,1:03:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子已经关门在搞维修了\NLooks like it's close for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.48,1:03:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 这边\NOkay, this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.12,1:03:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.80,1:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣若望洗礼堂
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.52,1:03:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗礼盆\NThe baptismal font.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.69,1:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是但丁\NDante again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.77,1:04:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是但丁 为什么是但丁\NAlways Dante, why Dante?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.67,1:04:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 丙烯底涂料 - 你指颜料吗\N- Acrylic gesso. - You mean paint.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.51,1:04:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水性颜料\NWater soluble paint.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.60,1:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闻着像是落水狗\NSmells like a wet dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.03,1:04:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那 有笔迹\NLook at that. There's a writing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.79,1:04:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"寻找那位欺诈的威尼斯总督\N"Seek the treacherous Doge of Venice,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.48,1:04:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他曾切断马匹之头" - 威尼斯\N- who severed the heads from horses." - Venice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.09,1:04:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但丁在那儿身染虐疾 最终客死异乡\NWhere Dante was infected with the disease that killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.30,1:04:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"跪在金碧辉煌的神圣智慧博学园内\N"Kneel within the gilded museum of holy wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.92,1:04:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聆听小溪的流水之声"\Nand listen for the sounds of trickling water."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.79,1:04:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"下到水下宫殿深处\N"Follow deep into the sunken palace,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.88,1:04:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 冥府怪物就在此间等待" - 说的是病毒\N- where the chthonic monster waits." - The plague itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.26,1:05:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水面以下\NUnderwater.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.18,1:05:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"淹没在血红的水下\N"Submerged in the blood-red waters of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.56,1:05:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那里的泻湖不会倒映群星" - 教授\N- of the lagoon that reflects no stars." - Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.22,1:05:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你能告诉我你到底在搞什么鬼吗\NCould you please tell me what the hell you are doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.61,1:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你还不来帮忙\NWhy haven't you called in?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.16,1:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.42,1:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克里斯托夫·布沙尔 世界卫生组织\NChristoph Bouchard, from the World Health Organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.66,1:05:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们见过的 - 我们见过\N- We've met. - We've met?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.39,1:05:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的不记得了么 才过了两天\NYou really don't remember? It was just 2 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.71,1:05:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他头部受伤 这是副作用\NHe's suffering the effects of a head wound.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.94,1:05:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法记起过去两天发生的事情\NHe can't remember the events for the last 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.31,1:05:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是飞到剑桥向你寻求帮助的那位 (译注: 哈佛大学位于美国剑桥市)\NI'm the one who flew to Cambridge and asked for your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.75,1:05:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给了你指示器 你负责解密\NI gave you the pointer to decode.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.42,1:05:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登先生\NMr. Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.95,1:05:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.15,1:05:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我想起来了\NOkay. I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.53,1:05:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.57,1:06:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是教授在医院里救助时急诊室的医生\NI was the ER doctor at the hospital when the Professor came in.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.76,1:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最后能记起来的事情是什么\NWhat is the last thing you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.12,1:06:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在大街上 我觉得就在这里\NI was on the street. I think it was here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.28,1:06:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还陪着位女士\NI was with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.32,1:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 然后被注射了东西 - 伊丽莎白·辛斯基\N- And I was given an injection. - Elizabeth Sinskey.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.71,1:06:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白\NElizabeth?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.07,1:06:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是世卫组织的\NFrom the World Health Organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.99,1:06:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识她么\NDo you know her?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.68,1:06:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.05,1:06:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我好几年没见过她了\NBut I haven't seen Elizabeth in years.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.69,1:06:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是我单独跟着你们的原因\NShe's the reason I followed you alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.46,1:06:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.41,1:06:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信辛斯基博士正与外国政府协作\NI believe Dr. Sinskey is working with a foreign government
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.78,1:06:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在合力寻找并外销病毒\Nto find and sell the virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.66,1:06:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 那不可能\NNo. No. No. That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.93,1:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人是会变的 教授\NPeople change, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.81,1:06:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经追捕贝特朗·佐布里斯特两年了\NI've been chasing Bertrand Zobrist for 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.46,1:06:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有人在竭力反对我\NAnd someone has been working against me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.41,1:06:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们讲重点 你知道病毒在哪里吗\NLet's get to the point. You know where the virus is?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.50,1:06:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你应该有身份证明吧\NI assume you have some sort of credentials.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.79,1:06:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问WHO的话你请便\NCall WHO if you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.58,1:06:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查一下我 但动作快点\NCheck me out, but do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.11,1:07:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尼斯 我觉得在威尼斯\NVenice. We think it's Venice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.45,1:07:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.68,1:07:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐火车要两小时 跟我来吧\NIt's 2 hours by train. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.94,1:07:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能找到你 别人也可以\NIf I could find you, so can the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.68,1:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你们都买张去日内瓦的机票\NI'm buying you both plane tickets to Geneva.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.16,1:07:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是日内瓦 他说是威尼斯\NNo, not Geneva. He said Venice.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.75,1:07:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了\NI heard that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.09,1:07:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一下 请大家注意\NExcuse us. Please watch yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.14,1:07:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请退后 让一下\NStep back, please. Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.83,1:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一下\NExcuse us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.18,1:07:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家注意\NWatch yourself, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.91,1:07:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是飞日内瓦的班机吗 - 是的 不过登机口刚刚关闭了\N- This is the plane to Geneva? - Yes, but we just closed the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.59,1:07:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让飞机待那别动 我们要检查全部乘客\NKeep the plane at the gate. We need to check every passenger.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.61,1:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是在浪费时间了\NThat would be a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.28,1:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们的时间很紧\NAnd we have very little of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.05,1:07:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往威尼斯的Italo 9982次动车 下午 1:57
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.90,1:07:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天前 在历经两年的追查后 我们找到了佐布里斯特\N3 days ago, after 2 years of searching, I found Zobrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.48,1:08:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他然后自杀了 但我们在他口袋里找到一个包裹\NHe killed himself. But we took a package from his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.31,1:08:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是什么\NAnd what was in it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.51,1:08:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装有"地狱图"的法拉第指示器\NThe Faraday pointer with the map of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.51,1:08:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个谜题 专门为其拥护者解谜而设计的\NA puzzle, specifically designed for his followers to solve.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.13,1:08:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把它交给了你\NWe brought it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.77,1:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你正在解密的时候\NAnd you were in the process of decoding it,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.58,1:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人给绑架了\Nwhen you were kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.57,1:08:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授\NProfessor Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.04,1:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你当时跟辛斯基博士在一块 - 伊丽莎白 对的\N- You were with Dr. Sinskey at the time. - Elizabeth, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.08,1:08:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有没有向你透露任何对病毒感兴趣的第三方组织\NDid she tell you about any third party interest in the virus?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.08,1:08:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不记得了 - 她在经济上是不是有困难\N- I don't remember. - Did she have financial problems?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.99,1:08:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我不知道\NUh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.16,1:08:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有没有带着备用手机\NDid she carry more than one cellphone?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.81,1:08:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.79,1:08:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 想一下 - 他不记得了\N- Think. - He doesn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.92,1:08:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就告诉我谁能记得 教授 "不知道 不记得" 真是够了\NThen tell me who can remember, Professor! Enough with the "I don't know, I don't remember."!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.40,1:08:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样对他不好\NIt's not good for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.01,1:08:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个"金碧辉煌的博学园"是在威尼斯圣马可大教堂内\NThe "gilded museum" is that Saint Mark's.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.70,1:08:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个威尼斯都是博学园\NAll of Venice is a museum.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.52,1:09:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿有"圣马尔谷之马"雕塑 它们都是铜像\NSt. Mark's has the Horses of Constantinople, they're bronze statues.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.02,1:09:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以看看吗\NCan I see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.68,1:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我我就不会碰它\NI wouldn't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.61,1:09:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不打算那样\NI wasn't planning on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.90,1:09:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授\NProfessor.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.62,1:09:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授\NProfessor Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.43,1:09:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授\NProfessor Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.21,1:09:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授\NProfessor Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.14,1:09:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.13,1:09:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 罗伯特\NHello, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.16,1:09:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白\NElizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.13,1:09:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见\NIt's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.52,1:09:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太久了\NToo long.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.34,1:09:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么风把你吹来了\NWhat brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.06,1:09:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WHO需要你的帮助\NThe WHO needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.44,1:09:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的帮助\NMy help?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.57,1:10:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你还记得但丁\NI hope you still remember your Dante.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.60,1:10:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚发生了什么\NWhat just happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.01,1:10:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NAre you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.75,1:10:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能弄点水吗 他可能脱水了\NCould you get some water? He could be dehydrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.63,1:10:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄点吃的 或者水果 或者列车上别的什么\NSome food, maybe some fruit or something from the machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.66,1:10:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快点 - 好的\N- Quickly. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.56,1:10:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.10,1:10:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他在撒谎吗 - 他在撒谎\N- Is he lying? - Through his teeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.75,1:10:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是那天来找我的人\NHe was not the one who came to Cambridge to see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.62,1:10:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布沙尔 快来帮我 快点 我觉得他虚脱了\NBouchard, I need help, quickly. I think he's collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.39,1:11:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这门我打不开\NI can't open the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.93,1:11:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登\NLangdon?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.26,1:11:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.71,1:11:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登 你还好吗\NLangdon, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.55,1:11:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 咱们走\NCome on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.54,1:11:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在告诉我过去两年来\NYou're telling me that for 2 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.25,1:11:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的组织都在跟我作对吗\Nyou and your organization have been working against me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.51,1:11:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\NThat is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.67,1:11:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩饰贝特朗·佐布里斯特和他的研究\NTo shield Bertrand Zobrist and his research.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.25,1:11:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 藏着他 保护他 - 很遗憾 是的\N- To hide him, to protect him. - Regrettably, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.58,1:11:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我全部的 避免他引发全球性流行病的尝试\NAnd that all of my attempts to prevent him from initiating
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.96,1:11:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因为你们在从中作梗而失败了\Na worldwide pandemic have failed because of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.11,1:11:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单概括的话 是的\NAn incisive sum-up, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.53,1:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你又冒冒失失的跑来 要求我相信你\NNow you have the temerity to ask that I simply decide to trust you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.79,1:12:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 在我看来 别无他法\NI'm terribly sorry, I didn't see any other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.61,1:12:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的团队 到底是干什么的\NWho exactly does your group work for?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.51,1:12:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是服务于客户\NOur clients, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.64,1:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一家私人安保公司 运作得很成功\NWe are a private security firm. A very successful one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.83,1:12:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以请问一下\NMay I ask,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.32,1:12:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前与你共事的那位绅士 布沙尔探员\Nthe gentleman who was with you, agent Bouchard,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.27,1:12:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在在哪儿\Nwhere is he now?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.44,1:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不得而知 他已经失去行踪了\NWe don't know. We lost track of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.49,1:12:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在的情况要比你们想像的还糟\NThen the situation is worse than you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.87,1:12:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有唯一一种原因会令他选择失联\NThere is only one reason he would move out of contact,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.71,1:12:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要独自找到兰登先生\Nhe wants Mr. Langdon to himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.86,1:12:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.80,1:12:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到病毒 然后再抬价转手 我猜的\NTo find the virus and sell it to the highest bidder I assume.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.01,1:12:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借贷收购 敲诈勒索 你懂的 老一套\NLeverage, blackmail, you know, the usual shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.11,1:12:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得咱们不必再深入讨论了 西姆斯先生\NI don't think we have anything further to discuss, Mr. Sims.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.27,1:12:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找病原体的时间已经不足8小时 抱歉\NAnd I have less than 8 hours to find this pathogen, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.58,1:13:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我所知 在此之前你就认识教授\NFrom what I understand, you knew the Professor sometime ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.72,1:13:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有过私交\NPersonally.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.06,1:13:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在乎他\NYou care about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.26,1:13:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甚至会为了保护他 而跟像我这种不择手段的人合作 不是吗\NYou would even ally with an unscrupulous character\Nsuch as myself to protect him, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.33,1:13:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的组织就有找到兰登教授的资源\NMy organization has the resources to find your Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.80,1:13:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尼斯 意大利 下午 2:49
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.68,1:13:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你想要散播瘟疫 这儿就是理想之地\NIf you wanted to start a plague, this is where you do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.85,1:13:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.68,1:13:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿每年有两千万游客来自全球各地的游客\N20 million people a year come here from every corner of the globe.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.56,1:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,14世纪黑死病肆虐期间 威尼斯人号令全部船只\NDuring the Black Death, the Venetians made all the ships
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.52,1:14:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在港口抛锚停泊40天\Nanchored in the harbor for 40 days,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.41,1:14:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随后才允许船员入城\Nbefore they would allow the crews into the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.51,1:14:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以确保瘟疫不会传入城内\NMaking sure that they were not carrying the Plague.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.45,1:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英文中"隔离"一词就是来自意大利语\NThe word "Quarantine" comes from the Italian.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.64,1:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有"四十" 来自"Quaranta"\N"quaranta", "forty".
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.77,1:14:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你陪同感觉很棒呢 教授\NIt's nice to have you back, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.31,1:14:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿 马雕在那儿 (圣马尔谷之马)\NThere, the horses.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.09,1:14:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是复制品 原件在圣殿内部保管 (原因: 空气污染)\NThese were recreations, the originals are in a museum for preservation.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.08,1:14:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧了 布沙尔知道我们会到这儿\NWe should be quick. Bouchard knows we are coming here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.19,1:14:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.11,1:14:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问一下那位导游 这些雕塑的马头有没有被切下过\NAsk that guide, if the heads have ever been severed from these horses?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.90,1:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下 打扰一下\NExcuse me. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.96,1:14:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 打扰一下 - 麻烦了 打扰一下\N- Excuse me. - Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.81,1:14:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.71,1:14:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说在第四次十字军东征期间(1202年 - 1204年)\NAccording to the tale, during the Crusades,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.42,1:15:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些马雕被威尼斯军队从拜占庭的君士坦丁堡(今伊斯坦布尔)劫走\Nthe horses were looted from Constantinople.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.59,1:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马匹...\NHorses...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.21,1:15:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它们实在太大 难以装船\NBut they were too large to be loaded on board the ships,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.34,1:15:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以马头被切下 随后再重新接回\Nso their heads were removed and reattached.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.82,1:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位总督干的\NBy whom?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.75,1:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位长生不老的总督 恩里科·丹多洛 (第41任威尼斯总督)\NThe doge who lived forever, Enrico Dandolo.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.33,1:15:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 恩里科·丹多洛 - 长生不老的总督\N- Enrico Dandolo. - The doge who lived forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.21,1:15:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 恩里科·丹多洛\NOf course, Enrico Dandolo.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.83,1:15:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹多洛把威尼斯人骗入十字军中\NDandolo tricked the Venetians into the Crusades.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.11,1:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他原本应当率众前往埃及 却跑去把君士坦丁堡给洗劫了\NHe was supposed to sail his ships to Egypt, but he sacked Constantinople instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.01,1:15:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 当然是他了\NI'm sorry. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.17,1:15:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"金碧辉煌的神圣智慧博学园"\N"The gilded museum of holy wisdom."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.80,1:15:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找错了教堂吗\NAre we in the wrong basilica?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.81,1:15:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找错了国家\NWe're in the wrong country.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.52,1:15:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹多洛逝世后 并没有埋葬在此\NDandolo passed, but he was not buried here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.83,1:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他葬在哪里\NSo where was he buried?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.48,1:15:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣索菲亚大教堂\NHagia Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.74,1:15:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 伊斯坦布尔 - 伊斯坦布尔 (土耳其)\N- Istanbul. - Istanbul.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.20,1:16:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总会有出路的\NThere's always a way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.27,1:16:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿 这儿\NHere. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.83,1:16:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你能不能把那个打开来\NSee if you could get that open.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.72,1:16:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抓住你的脚了\NI got your foot.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.50,1:17:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能搞定吗\NCan you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.55,1:17:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外头有人吗\NIs there someone there?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.81,1:17:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮一下\NPlease help.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.06,1:17:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.59,1:17:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉我一把\NGive me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.25,1:17:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 100块 - 好的 好的\N- One hundred. - Yes! Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.57,1:17:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 100欧元 - 给 我有 我有的\N- A hundred euro. - Here. I got it. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.56,1:17:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快 快\NQuick. Quick. Quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.06,1:18:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.39,1:18:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.25,1:18:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过他是个谋杀犯 是个精神变态\NYou called him a murderer, a psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.73,1:18:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.12,1:18:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但历史会把我们视为救世主\NBut history will call us saviors.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.72,1:18:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 我的天呐\NOh my god. Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.06,1:19:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怕死 罗伯特\NI'm not afraid to die, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.56,1:19:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但无所事事才是令我害怕的\NBut doing nothing terrifies me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.33,1:19:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指引 指示器 他是要留给你的 佐布里斯特\NThe path, and the pointer, he left that all for you, Zobrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.66,1:19:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你认识他吗 - 何止认识\N- You knew him? - Knew him?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.20,1:19:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱他\NI loved him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.91,1:19:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这套衣服就是他的\NYou're wearing his suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.21,1:19:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 西恩娜 不\NNo. Sienna, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.63,1:19:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 罗伯特\NThank you, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.82,1:19:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你做的一切\NThank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.36,1:19:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 西恩娜 不要\NNo. No. Sienna, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.84,1:19:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西恩娜\NSienna!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.90,1:19:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 西恩娜 西恩娜 不要\NNo, Sienna! Sienna, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.84,1:20:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢点 慢点 你太快啦\NSlow down, slow down. You're too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.87,1:20:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 拜托 拜托\NOh, come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.94,1:20:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个费了我三天时间\NThis took me 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.21,1:20:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太简单啦\NToo easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.99,1:20:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"镀金时代" - 马克·吐温\N"The Gilded Age" by Mark Twain
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.29,1:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢\NI love it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.09,1:21:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识你之前\NEverything before you exist,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.68,1:21:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美生活还是臆想\Nan idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.98,1:21:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今已经成真了\NAnd now it's real.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.11,1:21:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱 让 灵魂 复苏\NLove awaken the soul to act.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.89,1:21:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不公平 拿但丁来比喻我\NThat's not fair. Quoting Dante to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.61,1:21:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过诗句里是"美" 而不是"爱"\NBut it's beauty, not love.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.15,1:21:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.91,1:22:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离午夜还差一分钟\NIt's a minute to midnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.89,1:22:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我预想的还要早\NSooner than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.16,1:22:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去哪\NWhere're we going?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.57,1:22:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.64,1:22:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.18,1:22:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一同策划 一同构思\NWe planned it together, we designed it together,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.87,1:22:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这部分只有你才知晓\Nbut this part only belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.41,1:22:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道在哪 才会更安全\NIt's just safer if you don't know where.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.52,1:22:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们抢先找到了你呢\NWhat if they find you first?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.10,1:22:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时怎么办\NWhat then?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.20,1:22:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想知道 你也不是一个人\NIf you want to know, you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.99,1:23:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得开始相信我\NYou got to start by trusting me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.18,1:23:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们若不立即采取大胆行动\NUnless we take bold immediate action
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.34,1:23:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六次大灭绝就会轮到我们头上\Nthe sixth extinction will be our own.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.81,1:23:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.34,1:23:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给你安排另一条路\NI'm going to make you another path.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.99,1:23:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱也在尽头\NInferno will be at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.26,1:23:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我遇到不测 第一条线索就会发给你\NIf something should happen to me, the first clue will be deliver to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.57,1:23:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你会做好必须要做的事情\NI know you'll do what must to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.97,1:23:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找 就寻见\NSeek and find.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.14,1:23:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一个人\NYou're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.50,1:24:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\NSo.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.20,1:25:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮的小妮子跑去找坏家伙了\NThe beautiful young woman went for the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.66,1:25:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事常常发生\NThat happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.04,1:25:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看着好失望呢\NYou look disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.75,1:25:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先让你缓一缓\NI'll give you a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.37,1:25:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白并非是想要转卖病毒的人\NElizabeth is not the one who wants the virus to sell.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.96,1:25:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人是你\NYou are.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.58,1:25:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被人利用了\NYou've been used.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.41,1:25:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在精心计划 驱使你为他们效力\NElaborate schemes created by people to get you to do what they want.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.72,1:25:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于我\NBut me,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.13,1:25:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就简单粗暴了\NI'm very direct.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.94,1:25:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我正掌握一个绝佳的机会\NAnd this is a moment of great opportunity for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.71,1:25:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 病毒在哪里\NSo, where is the virus?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.97,1:25:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 教授\NCome on, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.52,1:25:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人世间生命几何\NHow much life is there in the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.00,1:25:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少生来就在困苦挣扎\NHow much more is fighting to be born?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.46,1:25:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔自相残杀也并无过错\NNothing wrong with thinning the herd once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.40,1:26:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很正常\NIt's healthy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.21,1:26:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已见过许多天意\NI've seen many acts of god.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.97,1:26:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 台风 霍乱 你知道吗\NI mean, typhoons, cholera. And you know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.80,1:26:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候带走的 还是善人之命\NSometimes it hits the right people.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.28,1:26:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 惨无人性 - 人之常情本就是不人道的\N- That's inhuman. - Humanity is inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.00,1:26:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人命或许轻贱 但从未有人停止过\NLife maybe cheap, but the means to end it on a mass scale,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.50,1:26:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探求灭绝众生的方法手段\Nno one ever stops paying for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.89,1:26:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再最后问你一...\NI'm going to ask you for the last...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.60,1:26:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分抱歉\NTerribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.44,1:26:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没别的法子了\NDidn't see any other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.64,1:26:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须得迅雷不及掩耳 见血越少 效果越好\NMust do this quickly. The less blood the better.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.65,1:27:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪位\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.51,1:27:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 一名协作者\NOh, a facilitator.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.14,1:27:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了别的业务 我们公司还制造幻觉\NAmong other things my company creates illusions.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.38,1:27:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头部并没有受伤\NYou never had a real head wound.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.07,1:27:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但我失忆了 - 是化学作用\N- But I lost my memory. - Chemically induced.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.07,1:27:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给你注射的是苯二氮䓬类药物 (精神药物)\NWe gave you an injection of benzodiazapenes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.11,1:27:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 会伴有皮疹 一两天后就消退\NSorry, it can produce a skin rash. It should fade in a day or so.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.57,1:27:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是...\NAll this was a...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.77,1:27:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是假的吗\NAll this was a fake?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.38,1:27:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜欢制造真实感\NI prefer created reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.47,1:27:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手下绑架了你\NMy agents kidnapped you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.73,1:27:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了触发全新的剧情 他们消去了你的记忆\NThey cleared your memories so we could create a fresh scenario,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.47,1:27:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由此你便投身于协助我们的思路中\Nwhereby you would be invested in the idea of helping us.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.40,1:27:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在你头皮上划了一道小口子 这是枪击幻觉的一部分\NA small incision was made in your scalp to give the impression of a bullet graze.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.67,1:27:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医院里的门也是假锁的\NThere are no locks on hospital doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.25,1:28:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\NExactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.98,1:28:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满分回答\NHighest marks.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.31,1:28:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医院里杀人的那位女警察呢\NWhat about the policewoman who shot the Doctor in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.80,1:28:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我的人\NAlso it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.06,1:28:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的枪里是空包弹\NHer gun fired blanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.32,1:28:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门上则有爆炸伪造的枪击效果\NAnd there were squibs in the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.57,1:28:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生是演员 身上挂着袋血浆包\NThe doctor was an agent wearing a blood packet.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.67,1:28:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租车司机 整个医院都是咱们的人\NThe taxi driver, the hospital was working for us as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.00,1:28:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旧宫里她试图要杀了我\NAt the Palazzo Vecchio she tried to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.43,1:28:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是真枪实弹\NIt was real bullets.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.92,1:28:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要求的\NAt my behest.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.89,1:28:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当事情快要败露时\NWhen things that appeared to go tits up
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.34,1:28:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会试图赶紧杀人灭口 毁尸灭迹\NI try to sweep it all away quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.50,1:28:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要杀我\NBy killing me?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.80,1:28:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深表歉意 兰登先生\NI apologize unreservedly, Mr. Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.48,1:28:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确失去了一名老部下\NI did lose an experienced agent.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.33,1:28:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个行当里 我见过的情况够多了\NThere's a great deal of situation I've been informed in my line of work.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.09,1:28:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 我知道的就这些\NLook, hear me what I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.91,1:28:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我看着很渗人\NI know I've behaved terribly.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.42,1:29:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但谜题需要破解 这一点你最棒了\NBut a puzzle needed solving, who better to solve it than you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.72,1:29:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞟一眼 好吗\NGlance at it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.02,1:29:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得差强人意了\NNot my best work.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.84,1:29:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但足以应付意大利人\NBut it will do for the Italians.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.39,1:29:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西恩娜来找我求助的时候 佐布里斯特早已拥趸者众\NZobrist had followers everywhere when Sienna first came to me for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.55,1:29:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我是这么认为的\NOr so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.53,1:29:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐布里斯特死后不久 她就很严肃地找上门来\NShe came to us with serious concerns shortly after Zobrist died.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.20,1:29:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎的 她知道了我们受雇于佐布里斯特\NSomehow, she knew Zobrist had hired us.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.40,1:29:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她表示这位富翁的生物研究成果 可能已经落到坏人手中\NShe said he was doing biological work that could be fallen into the wrong hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.07,1:29:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她并未提及瘟疫 但我们已经开始警惕\NShe didn't mention a plague. But we heard enough to be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.25,1:29:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我们同意协助她 找到佐布里斯特的计划\NSo we agreed to work with her to find Zobrist's project.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.15,1:29:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后当辛斯基博士带你来时 我们看到了机会\NAnd when Dr. Sinskey brought you in, we saw an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.81,1:30:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时是伊丽莎白来找我的\NIt was Elizabeth who came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.08,1:30:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.43,1:30:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从布沙尔探员手上 辛斯基博士弄到了法拉第指示器\NDr. Sinskey got the Faraday pointer from agent Bouchard.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.40,1:30:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她带去让你解密\NShe brought it to you to decode,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.64,1:30:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至用你的指纹来设作密码\Nand she even secured it with your thumbprint.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.50,1:30:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们别无选择\NThat left us with no choice,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.94,1:30:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们在街上把你抢了过来\Nso we took you from her on the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.42,1:30:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医院里的情况促使你相信布鲁克斯医生\NThe hospital scenario encouraged you to trust Dr. Brooks.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.70,1:30:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们给领事馆打电话时 另一头接通的是我们\NWhen you called to the Consulate it was answered by our man.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.23,1:30:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登教授\NProfessor Langdon?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.76,1:30:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地你还活着 我们一直在找你\NThank heavens you're alive. We've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.43,1:30:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西你还带着吗\NAre you still in possession?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.75,1:30:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带着指示器 我们跟着你\NYou had the pointer and we had you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.80,1:30:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都推进的天衣无缝 直到布鲁克斯女士把你引开\NIt was all working seamlessly until Miss. Brooks stole you away.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.72,1:30:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以确保病毒得以释放\NTo make sure the virus is released.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.00,1:30:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来\NIt appears.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.66,1:30:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人很失望\NYoung people are disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.74,1:30:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现他们35岁左右时 就挺有耐性的了\NI find them become tolerable around 35.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.77,1:30:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你提到过辛斯基博士\NYou mentioed Dr. Sinskey.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.72,1:31:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很担心你\NI've been so worried.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.35,1:31:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NAre you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.13,1:31:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我很好 - 是吗\N- I'm fine. - Are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.45,1:31:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好\NI'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.72,1:31:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的\NI'm alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.65,1:31:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\NThank god.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.80,1:31:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你知道病毒在哪儿吗 - 伊斯坦布尔\N- Do you know where the virus is? - Istanbul.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.96,1:31:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界卫生组织专机 下午 5:32
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.60,1:31:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是时候\NNow's the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.07,1:31:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是重生之日\NToday is rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.55,1:31:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱就是救赎\NInferno is salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.49,1:31:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉把你卷进来 罗伯特\NI am so sorry I brought you into this, Robert,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.93,1:31:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 在这么多年之后 - 没事 我很高兴你那么做了\N- after all these years. - No. I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.92,1:31:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过他 佐布里斯特 两年前\NI met him, you know. Zobrist, 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.51,1:31:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当时向我求助\NHe asked for my help.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.26,1:31:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想让WHO支持他的行动\NHe wanted the WHO to endorse mass sterilization
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.61,1:32:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对饮用水和主食中进行大规模杀菌消毒\Nin drinking waters and staple foods.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.24,1:32:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我下了逐客令 把他列为监控对像\NSo I threw him out of my office, put him on the watch list.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.24,1:32:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他失踪了...\NBut he disappeared and...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.25,1:32:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜那就是他雇佣了西姆斯的时候\NI suppose that's when Zobrist hired Sims.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.55,1:32:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早应该发... 我不知道\NI should probably have... have I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.85,1:32:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.63,1:32:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都不是你的错 你总要为它们责怪自己\NYou always blame yourself for things that weren't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.00,1:32:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴还是很甜\NStill very sweet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.66,1:32:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 有个门口\NHere, a doorway.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.47,1:33:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望见面那会 是别的事情呢\NI wish it would have happened differently, back then.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.43,1:33:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们当时没有经营好 就这么散了\NWe didn't look after it. It fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.70,1:33:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是后悔吗\NIs that a regret?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.88,1:33:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来的时候才会这样\NOnly when I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.23,1:33:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗 在门口那发生的最有意思的事情是\NYou know, the most interesting things happened in doorways,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.90,1:33:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样一种持续的临界状态\Nat the borders, right along the edges.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.04,1:33:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古代渔民会在寒暖洋流交汇处打渔\NAncient fishermen learned to sail where the warm water met the cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.83,1:33:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鱼会滞留在暖流边上\NThe little fish would reach the edge of the warm water and they stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.24,1:33:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后大鱼就从寒流里游过来 把它们吃掉\NAnd the big fish would come out of the cold water and they eat them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.18,1:33:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是渔民们\NAnd the fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.01,1:33:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 渔翁得利\NWell, they caught everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.08,1:33:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门口那儿\NDoorways.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.27,1:34:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是老样子 罗伯特\NNot one part of you has changed, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.68,1:34:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话痨一个\NYou talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.76,1:34:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一点也没变\NAnd then, not at all
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.19,1:34:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白\NElizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.50,1:34:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法请求你别去日内瓦\NI couldn't ask you not to go to Geneva.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.30,1:34:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到\NI couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.73,1:34:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想让你离开剑桥市\NI didn't want to ask you to leave Cambridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.95,1:34:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就是这么发生的吗\NWas that how it happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.05,1:34:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再相信记忆了\NI don't trust my memory anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.61,1:34:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未忘记任何事情\NI never forget anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.98,1:34:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那是天赋\NWell, that's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.10,1:34:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的\NNo, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.85,1:35:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离他远点 嘿 嘿 你们在干嘛\NLeave him alone! Hey! Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.85,1:35:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离他远点\NLeave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.86,1:35:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过身去\NTurn around!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.76,1:35:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我 贱货 转过头去\NDon't look at me, bitch, look away!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.07,1:35:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手\NStop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.20,1:35:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看\NDon't look!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.75,1:35:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特\NRobert!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.96,1:35:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯坦布尔 土耳其 傍晚 6:39
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.51,1:35:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.70,1:36:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯坦布尔大学
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.64,1:36:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是诗人的朋友\NI'm a friend of the poet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.79,1:36:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐布里斯特为之舍身的是\NFor what did Zobrist die?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.01,1:36:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保全他人得生\NThat others may live.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.77,1:36:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我千里迢迢赶来 是要保证一切顺利进行\NI've come very far to make sure nothing interferes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.20,1:37:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们设计好的传送系统 会在今晚午夜释放病毒药剂\NThe delivery system we designed will discharge the viral agent by midnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.31,1:37:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有人正赶来要阻止这一切\NBut there are others who are on their way to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.92,1:37:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得抢先找到它\NI need to find it before they do
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.45,1:37:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引爆炸弹 确保病毒被释放\Nand trigger an explosion to ensure it's released.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.03,1:37:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们如何帮忙\NHow do we help?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.52,1:37:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在查士丁尼大瘟疫期间\NDuring the Plague of Justinian,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.99,1:37:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯坦布尔每天有5000人死于街头\N5000 people died everyday in the streets in Istanbul.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.03,1:37:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西方交流的又一个门户\NA border between East and West, another doorway.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.46,1:37:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他选中此地的原因\NWhich is why he chose it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.07,1:37:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果袋子没有破损 我们可以装住它\NIf the bag is intact, we can contain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.26,1:37:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若有人先发制人 把它弄破了\NBut if someone ruptures it before we get there
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.76,1:37:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,47天内 95%的地球人口会受感染\N95% of the earth's population will be infected in 47 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.10,1:37:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣索菲亚大教堂 傍晚 7:53
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.56,1:38:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授 博士\NProfessor. Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.58,1:38:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是米尔沙特 这儿的负责人\NMy name is Mirsat, I'm the curator here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.93,1:38:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有彻底疏散建筑内的人群\NHave you completely evacuated the building?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.17,1:38:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们竭尽全力了 但这地方实在太大\NWell, to the extent that we can but the place is massive.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.67,1:38:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以告诉我要找的东西具体是什么吗\NCould you tell me specifically what it is you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.42,1:38:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩里科·丹多洛之墓\NThe tomb of Enrico Dandolo.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.62,1:38:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 这边请\NOf course, this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.23,1:38:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"跪在金碧辉煌的神圣智慧博学园内\N"Kneel within the gilded museum of holy wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.62,1:38:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聆听小溪的流水声"\Nand listen for the sounds of trickling water."
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.03,1:39:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"下到水下宫殿深处"\N"Follow deep into the sunken palace."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.02,1:39:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到地面下有流水声\NI hear water flowing under these stones.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.04,1:39:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它流向哪儿\NWhere does it go?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.96,1:39:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个排水道 流入到市政蓄水池里\NIt's just drainage. It goes to the city cistern.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.20,1:39:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要找的是一个大型地下空间\NWe're looking for a large, underground space,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.47,1:39:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内部可能有支柱和人工照明\Nperhaps with columns, artificially lit from within.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.42,1:39:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那简单 古人的供水系统\NThat's simple. The ancient system,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.86,1:39:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16世纪 沉没的宫殿\Nsixth century, Yerebatan Sarayi.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.73,1:39:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也被称为"地下水宫殿"\NAlso called, "The sunken palace."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.83,1:39:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我们去那儿\NTake us there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.37,1:39:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的话只会对应一样东西\NHis words can only mean one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.37,1:39:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉没的宫殿 地下水宫殿\NYerebatan Sarayi. The Sunken Palace.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.43,1:39:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们下去后 你就会看到了\NOnce we descend, you'll see exactly what he described.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.32,1:39:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么用\NHow do I use it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.00,1:39:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸物装在接线盒里\NThere's a cap in the padial integrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.41,1:39:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸装置也有个引爆按钮\NThe device also has a detonation button.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.87,1:39:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去个电话 就会引爆\NA call from this cellphone will trigger the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.35,1:39:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么点就能弄破袋子吗\NAnd that's enough to break the bag?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.24,1:39:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四面墙壁都是混凝土\NThe walls are cement all around.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.72,1:40:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这俩炸弹都要装上 两个角度 尽量分开\NYou need both bombs, different angles, as far apart as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.20,1:40:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就能弄破袋子\NThat's what break the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.66,1:40:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史书认为黑死病带来了苦难和死亡\NHistory says that the Black Plague caused misery and death.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.31,1:40:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并没有告知我们\NBut, what they don't tell us,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.61,1:40:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它也同样精简了人口 并孕育了文艺复兴运动\Nis that it also produced a leaner population, and gave birth to the Renaissance.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.48,1:40:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在全速奔向地狱的第七层\NWe are rushing as fast as we can into the seventh circle of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.27,1:40:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自取灭亡 却又有利可图\NSuicidal but profitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.92,1:40:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够短痛 何必长痛\NWhy is suffering later preferable to suffering now?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.64,1:40:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若我们欣然接受 然后痛苦或许就能解救我们\NWhat if we embrace it. And then maybe pain can save us.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.88,1:40:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听明白了 对吧 我看得出来\NYou're getting this, aren't you? I can see that you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.33,1:40:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我想知道的是我并非形单影只\NNow I need to know that I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.54,1:41:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人太特么多了\NToo many damn people.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.77,1:41:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地方选得很好\NHe has chosen well.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.08,1:41:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要所有进出蓄水池的管道分配图\NI need schematics of all conduits in and out of the cistern.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.55,1:41:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有全面隔离和控制方案\NFull isolation and containment protocols.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.63,1:41:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物理和化学屏蔽 外加... 等会\NPhysical and chemical barriers along with... Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.04,1:41:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是城内的供水系统吗\NThis is the city's water supply?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.89,1:41:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 现在不是了 已经现代化改造过\NOh, not anymore. We've modernized.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.97,1:41:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但里面的水就留在那儿\NBut there is water in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.15,1:41:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 最终慢慢渗入地下\NYes. It eventually filters down into the earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.39,1:41:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么这么多人\NBut why are all these people here?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.76,1:41:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是旅游景点了 那儿的演出很精彩\NIt is a tourist attraction. The acoustics are excellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.23,1:41:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就有夏至音乐会 很受欢迎\NTonight is the summer solstice concert, very popular.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.45,1:41:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们从世界各地赶来 欣赏盛会\NPeople come from all over the world to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.58,1:41:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他制造了一种生物气溶胶\NHe created a bioaerosol.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.76,1:41:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可以通过空气传播\NSo it will spread in the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.93,1:41:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 清空现场人群 - 不要\N- Empty the place. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.48,1:41:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围住那儿\NContain it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.71,1:41:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屏蔽附近所有信号 断绝信息进出\NJam all communications down there. No messages get in or out.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.33,1:41:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白\NGot it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.42,1:41:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们进去吧\NShall we go in?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.03,1:41:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特 你不必陪我们进去\NRobert, you don't have to go in there with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.12,1:42:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我要去的\NYes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.18,1:42:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"血红的泻湖不会倒映群星"\N"Blood-red waters of the lagoon that reflects no stars."
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.06,1:42:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷 这儿就像个迷宫\NMy god, this is a labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.29,1:42:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少块区域\NHow many sections?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.99,1:42:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多 教授 很多\NThere are dozens, Professor, dozens.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.69,1:42:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去找到它\NLet's find it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.23,1:42:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检查每个区域 每条柱子\NCheck every section, every column.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.12,1:42:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全要检查\NCheck them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.90,1:42:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散开来\NSpread out.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.80,1:42:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在切断手机信号\NCut off cellphone service now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.95,1:42:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 隔绝通讯 - 是 长管\N- No communications. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.11,1:43:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿有美国的联络人 我需要帮助\NThose are US contacts over here, I need some help.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.88,1:43:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 这边走 美杜莎\NHere. This way. Medusa.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.73,1:43:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希腊神话 为什么 (译注: 美杜莎是希腊神话中的女蛇妖)\NThe Greek spirits, why?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.98,1:43:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它属于希腊神话中的一个特定种类 地府鬼神\NIt belongs to a specific category of Greek spirits. Chthonic monsters.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.69,1:43:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 就这儿吗 - 是的\N- This is it? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.91,1:43:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颜色 柱子 跟视频上看到的一模一样\NThe color, the columns, it's exactly what we saw in the video
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.44,1:43:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这儿了 大家散开 检查柱子\NThis is the area, so spread out, check the pillars.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.43,1:43:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我负责墙边 - 各个角落\N- I'll take the wall line. - The corners.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.64,1:43:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走道下面\NUnder the walkway.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.11,1:43:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如有任何发现 立即向我报告\NIf you find anything, report to me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.46,1:43:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来照照这里 分秒必争\NLight it here, someone. Seconds matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.32,1:43:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下 打扰一下\NExcuse me. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.69,1:43:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 发生什么事了 - 先生 请你让开\N- What's going on? - Sir, I need you to step aside.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.03,1:43:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位请回避\NStep aside, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.39,1:44:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找着了 在这儿 那个角落里\NI got it. It's here. In this far corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.29,1:45:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.65,1:45:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生化小组尚未就位\NHazmat guys aren't set yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.57,1:45:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等不及了\NI can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.43,1:46:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧的 这玩意随时会破\NQuickly! This could break any moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.88,1:46:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西恩娜\NSienna!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.89,1:46:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西恩娜\NSienna!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.19,1:46:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是氮气吹洗装置 徒手操作吗\NThis is cube nitrogen purge. Without gloves access.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.81,1:46:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 应该可以 - 最好如此\N- It should. - It better.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.28,1:46:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西恩娜 西恩娜\NSienna. Sienna.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.26,1:46:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人多势众\NThere are too many of us down here!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.86,1:46:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抢不到袋子的\NYou won't get to that bag before we do!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.20,1:47:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 但我会确保它破掉\NNo. But I can make sure it breaks.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.29,1:47:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 别这么做 西恩娜 不要 你会滥杀无辜\NNo. Don't do this, Sienna, don't. You'll be murdering innocents.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.29,1:47:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 很多人会死去\NYes. People will die
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.20,1:47:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但危机得以避免\Na lot of them but the crisis will be averted.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.05,1:47:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是大自然的旨意\NIt's what nature demands.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.57,1:47:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人口危机问题不再只会缓解 而是一劳永逸的解决了\NThe problem won't just be slowed down, it would be solved permanently.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.41,1:47:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借生灵涂炭来拯救苍生 这是暴君的逻辑\NKilling billions to save lives. That's the logic of tyrants.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.58,1:47:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 为了更高的目标 人类... - 就算天才也不能有这种权利\N- For a greater good, humanity... - Geniuses don't come with extra rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.95,1:47:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他有责任去行他人所不能行之事\NNo, it comes with the responsibility to take action when others won't!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.73,1:47:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做点什么 行啊\NYou want to do something, fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.53,1:47:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把问题提出来 然后解决掉\NThen scream at the top of your lungs. An event and leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.10,1:47:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你爱这个物种 如果你爱这个星球\NIf you loved humanity, if you love this planet,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.55,1:47:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不惜一切去挽救它\Nyou would do anything to save it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.60,1:47:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类历史上那些极恶之罪都曾冠以爱的名义\NThe greatest sins in human history had been committed in the name of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.08,1:47:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没人会赞同这种看法\NNo one will look on this act and call it love.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.62,1:47:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类会延续的\NThey'll be alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.21,1:47:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人如何评价 又与我何干\NWhat does it matter what they say about us.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.90,1:47:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无信号\N<font color="#80ffff">No Signal</font>
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.60,1:49:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你在干什么\NHey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.95,1:49:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以\NDon't!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.35,1:50:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别射着箱子\NDon't shoot the box!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.45,1:50:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特 快闪开\NRobert, get clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.15,1:51:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗 你没事吧\NAre you alright? Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.00,1:51:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.16,1:51:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箱子在哪 箱子在哪\NWhere's the box. Where's the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.05,1:51:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它密封了 完好无损\NIt's contained, no breach.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.88,1:52:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒已被完全隔离\NThe virus has been completely contained.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.30,1:52:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒已被隔离\NThe virus has been contained.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.95,1:52:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 医疗小组全部进场 - 我们现在接管这儿的工作\N- All medical team come in . - We'll take it from now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.63,1:52:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍 目标已被隔离 准备转移\NI repeat. The target is contained, be prepared for transport.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.10,1:52:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有泄漏 重复一遍 没有泄漏\NThere is no leakage. I Repeat. There is no leakage.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.95,1:53:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她以为她在拯救世界\NShe thought she was saving the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.41,1:53:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也是这么想的\NSo did they all.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.10,1:53:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来要做什么\NSo, what would happen now?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.35,1:53:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会带回日内瓦做检测 把它隔离起来\NWe'll take it back to Geneva for test, put it in isolation.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.60,1:53:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要测出基因序列\NWe'll have to generate another geno sequences first
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.06,1:53:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再顺藤摸瓜 提出解决方案\Nto get an idea what we are dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.54,1:53:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来还有很多事要忙\NThere's a lot of work to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.28,1:53:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢 回去吗\NAnd you, Cambridge?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:49.91,1:53:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.50,1:53:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛斯基博士\NDr. Sinskey?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.25,1:54:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活又要把咱分开了\NLife tore us apart again.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.73,1:54:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像但丁和比阿特丽斯那样\NLike Dante and Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.37,1:54:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有东西要给你\NI have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.13,1:54:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被绑架那晚 我捡到了这个\NI picked this up the night you were taken.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.93,1:54:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得它对你似乎意味非凡\NI seem to remember it was important to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.23,1:54:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 是的没错\NYes. Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.45,1:54:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有没有想过 你我之间\NDo you ever think about what could happen
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.67,1:54:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会发生些什么\Nwith you and me?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.05,1:54:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想过\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.49,1:54:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜生活还得有点儿神秘感 教授\NI guess life must have it's mysteries, Professor,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.02,1:55:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是我们俩\Neven for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.80,1:55:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛罗伦萨 意大利 某天早上 9:00
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.25,1:55:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 打扰一下 你会讲英语吗 - 会的\N- ' Scusati, do you speak English? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.17,1:55:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有见到玛塔·阿尔瓦雷兹 那位工作人员\NHave you seen Marta Alvarez, the museum staff?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.14,1:55:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛塔现在不在这 她怀孕了\NMarta isn't here just now. She's had her baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.62,1:55:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怀孕了 啊呀 太棒了\NShe had her baby? Aw, that is great.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.61,1:55:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息\NGreat news.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.91,1:55:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你或许要通知某人该给但丁面具展位开灯了\NWell, you might tell someone that the lights on the Dante mask
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.05,1:55:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我几乎看不到呢\Nshould be turned on because I can barely see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.62,1:55:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾 先生 但丁面具不在这儿\NI'm sorry, sir, the Dante mask is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.88,1:55:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被盗了\NIt was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.31,1:56:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 真的吗 - 嗯 - 我刚还看着它呢\N- Really? - Um - I was just looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.00,1:56:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下\NExcuse me.
